  {title: "Old Time Rock and Roll", episode_number: "S12, Ep4", description: "\nOwen suggests the interns learn about breaking bad news to patients' families.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5093170/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Guess Who's Coming to Dinner", episode_number: "S12, Ep5", description: "\nMaggie leaves her dinner party and races to the hospital, so April takes over the cooking duties in an attempt to avoid Jackson. Meanwhile, Arizona is extremely anxious about meeting Callie's new girlfriend.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5134958/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The Me Nobody Knows", episode_number: "S12, Ep6", description: "\nA transfer resident arrives at the hospital. Meanwhile, Richard wants his relationship with Maggie to evolve; gossip follows a patient who mistakenly sent his sex tape to his congregation; and April presents a case involving a boy from the Middle East.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5060714/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Something Against You", episode_number: "S12, Ep7", description: "\nA high-stakes case is tackled by a team of doctors, and the atmosphere grows tense. Meanwhile, Bailey pressures Ben to evict their roommate; and Arizona enthusiastically reenters the dating scene with a new wingman.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5134980/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Things We Lost in the Fire", episode_number: "S12, Ep8", description: "\nAs the rumor mill around the hospital continues to spiral out of control, Grey Sloan Memorial is flooded with injured firefighters from a nearby wildfire. Maggie struggles to keep things with Andrew professional at work; meanwhile, Jo questions Alex's priorities. Also, Alex decides to make a big step in his life.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5109306/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The Sound of Silence", episode_number: "S12, Ep9", description: "\nMeredith is attacked by a patient, and Penny finds her injured. The staff of GreySloanMemorial is standing by Meredith trying to save her life.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5134994/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "All I Want Is You", episode_number: "S12, Ep10", description: "\nAs the hospital deals with Meredith's trauma, Callie and Maggie perform a risky, experimental surgery on Alex's 15-year-old patient against his professional opinion. Meanwhile, Owen and Nathan are still at odds with each other, and Maggie and Andrew's relationship continues to develop.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5174364/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Unbreak My Heart", episode_number: "S12, Ep11", description: "\nFlashbacks reveal the evolution of April and Jackson's relationship, beginning with their initial meeting, and the years-long process of one of Jackson's patients. Also, April finds out something life changing.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5470704/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "My Next Life", episode_number: "S12, Ep12", description: "\nA patient from Meredith's first surgery as an intern is re-admitted to the hospital with an aneurysm; Maggie thinks Richard knows about her relationship with Andrew; Arizona considers dating again.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5479956/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "All Eyez on Me", episode_number: "S12, Ep13", description: "\nMeridith, Jo, Bailey, Callie and Jackson head to a Veterans hospital for an spectacular yet unusual surgery. Meanwhile, a group of snobby cheerleaders come into the ER and Warren makes a risky decision.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5505500/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Odd Man Out", episode_number: "S12, Ep14", description: "\nRichard swaps pairings among the residents and attendings, baffling everyone. Meanwhile, Arizona makes a bold decision as she treats a woman who's carrying quadruplets; April faces a tough choice.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5505518/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "I Am Not Waiting Anymore", episode_number: "S12, Ep15", description: "\nJackson learns about April's pregnancy, while Alex and the team of doctors handles a long triple-organ transplant surgery. Meredith considers dating again, and Andrew insists on not receiving special treatment after he and Maggie go public.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5520906/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "When It Hurts So Bad", episode_number: "S12, Ep16", description: "\nMeredith takes a step forward with Will but quickly regrets it; Maggie senses a disconnection with Andrew; and Amelia reevaluates her relationship with Owen. Meanwhile, Catherine comes into town and really shakes things up with April and Jackson    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5520910/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "I Wear the Face", episode_number: "S12, Ep17", description: "\nApril and Arizona find themselves arguing in switched positions. Richard tries to stop Catherine interfering in others' lives. Meanwhile residents motivated to compete for a great research grant.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5467378/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "There's a Fine, Fine Line", episode_number: "S12, Ep18", description: "\nAfter a missing child forces the hospital into lockdown, Ben decides to operate on a pregnant mother without the proper surgical equipment. Miranda, as Chief, is faced with the repercussions of the event.    ", season_id: 2406, series_id: 10, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5505676/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
