  {title: "Damned If You Do...", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nPenguin is King of Gotham and after a shakeup at the GCPD, Detective James Gordon's moral compass wavers, as he seeks help from Penguin.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-09-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4369190/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Knock, Knock", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nGordon investigates the inmate escape from Arkham Asylum while Galavan plots his next move. Bruce's quest to unlock the secrets of his father's office leads him to an old family friend.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-09-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371142/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "The Last Laugh", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nGordon and Bullock hunt a nemesis from the past, which leads to a standoff between Jerome and Gordon; and a magic show at a Gotham Children's Hospital gala results in a hostage situation.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371144/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Strike Force", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nBarnes forms a task force with help from Gordon; Penguin is kept busy trying to fulfill a favor for Galavan; and Nygma asks Kringle out on a date.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371148/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Scarification", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nGalavan and Penguin join forces with a dangerous family in Gotham. Then, as the rivalry between the Waynes and the Galavans resurfaces, Gordon struggles to maintain order in the city.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371152/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "By Fire", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nAfter Bridgit Pike is kidnapped her brothers, a new spark of courage ignites within her, as she chooses to take control of her future. Meanwhile, Kringle and Nygma's relationship will take a new step and Penguin and Galavan continue to battle for control of Gotham City's underworld.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371154/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Mommy's Little Monster", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nButch leads Penguin and his men to the warehouse where Gertrude is being held, as Penguin plots his revenge on Galavan for kidnapping his mother.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371156/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Tonight's the Night", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nGalavan sends Barbara after Jim Gordon, while he tries to make a business deal with Bruce Wayne. Barnes and Bullock are hot on Barbara's trail, and Nygma has a run-in with a familiar face.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371166/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "A Bitter Pill to Swallow", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nGordon runs into a hitman known as Eduardo Flamingo; Penguin and Nygma have another encounter.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371158/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The Son of Gotham", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nGordon confronts a suspect who is connected to Galavan, but falls short of obtaining any information. Meanwhile, Bruce gets one step closer to discovering the name of his parents' killer.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371164/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Worse Than a Crime", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nJim Gordon turns to Dangerous Allies for assistance when Bruce Wayne is abducted.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371170/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Mr. Freeze", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nPenguin gives Gordon a hard time; a skilled cryogenics engineer named Victor Fries is involved in a body-snatching spree.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371172/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "A Dead Man Feels No Cold", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nGordon and Bullock look to Nora for help in their search for Victor, Penguin meets Hugo Strange.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371174/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "This Ball of Mud and Meanness", episode_number: "S2, Ep14", description: "\nAlfred and Selina help Bruce on his quest to find his parents' killer Matches Malone. Meanwhile, Gordon follows up with Edward Nygma on Kristin Kringle's whereabouts. Hugo Strange continues his treatment to reduce Penguin's aggression.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371254/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Mad Grey Dawn", episode_number: "S2, Ep15", description: "\nGordon and Bullock investigate a trail of clues left in a museum robbery which unbeknownst to them were left by Nygma in a dangerous game of cat and mouse. Gordon's past comes back to haunt him when an anonymous person threatens to expose his hand in Galavan's murder. Meanwhile Penguin's visit to some old friends leads him to meet his father Elijah Van Dahl (Paul Reubens). and Bruce practices his street smarts.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371252/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Prisoners", episode_number: "S2, Ep16", description: "\nAfter Gordon is removed from protective custody, he begins to face new threats and dangers inside prison walls. In order to survive he must rely on a new friend as well as Bullock and other outside help. Meanwhile, Penguin grows closer to his Father, while his step-mother and step-siblings move forward with their own plans for the family.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371250/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Into the Woods", episode_number: "S2, Ep17", description: "\nWhen a boy is found murdered on the Appalachian Trail, the BAU team goes deep into its forests in search of a man lurking in the wilderness who is targeting children.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-11-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371256/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Pinewood", episode_number: "S2, Ep18", description: "\nAfter leaving Arkham Asylum, Barbara attempts to make amends with Gordon. Bruce and Alfred track down one of Thomas Wayne's former friend's from project chimera, but Hugo Strange disrupts their plan.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371258/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Azrael", episode_number: "S2, Ep19", description: "\nGordon and Bruce question Professor Strange about project chimera which leads Strange to send the newly resurrected Galavan to confront Gordon. Meanwhile, Nygma investigates who Professor Strange is.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371262/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Unleashed", episode_number: "S2, Ep20", description: "\nAzrael is loose in Gotham city which sparks Penguin's need for revenge. Meanwhile, Bruce enlists Selina's help in tracking down Professor Strange as he evades arrest for his experiments.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371264/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "A Legion of Horribles", episode_number: "S2, Ep21", description: "\nHugo Strange welcomes a familiar face to Gotham after he resurrects Fish Mooney in Indian Hill. Meanwhile, Bruce discovers a friend is in danger and teams up with Gordon, Alfred and Lucius while uncovering more of his experiments.    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371270/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "Transference", episode_number: "S2, Ep22", description: "\nwhile Gordon, Bruce and Lucius remain at Indian Hill, the city of Gotham will be met with a new threat as Hugo Stranges inmates devise a plan to escape and start their new lives in Gotham    ", season_id: 2430, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4371272/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "The Legend Reborn", episode_number: "S1, Ep0", description: "\nFrom its comic book origins to cutting edge production, go behind the scenes of the highly anticipated TV show, Gotham with creator Bruno Heller and star Ben McKenzie.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: nil, seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5655200/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Pilot", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nJames Gordon and Harvey Bullock are assigned to track down the killer of Thomas and Martha Wayne.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3216414/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Selina Kyle", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nSomeone is kidnapping homeless kids. One of them is a young girl named Selina Kyle. Meanwhile, Oswald Cobblepot goes off the grid.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4017996/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "The Balloonman", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nA masked vigilante is killing off corrupt citizens by strapping them to weather balloons. Cobblepot returns to Gotham.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3993356/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Arkham", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nFalcone and Maroni fight over the Arkham section of Gotham. Cobblepot becomes the manager of Maroni's favorite restaurant.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3975220/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Viper", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nGordon and Bullock search for the source of a new street drug that causes euphoria then death. Meanwhile, Oswald Cobblepot works his way deeper into Maroni's inner circle and Fish Mooney continues to plot against Falcone.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3993362/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Spirit of the Goat", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nSomeone is killing rich children by taking on the name of The Goat, a serial killer that Harvey took down when he was young. Montoya and Allen finally have evidence against Gordon.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3993368/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Penguin's Umbrella", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nWord is out that Cobblepot is alive, leading Falcone and Maroni to the brink of war and causing Gordon to go on the run.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4033254/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The Mask", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nGordon and Bullock investigate a Gothamite who runs a deadly fight club for candidates applying for a job at his financial firm. Meanwhile, Bruce returns to school and gets a visit from a new friend.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4049582/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Harvey Dent", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nGordon teams up with a young attorney, named Harvey Dent, to find the Wayne family's killer. Russians break a former bomb maker out of prison. Selina goes to live at Wayne Manor.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4069154/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Lovecraft", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nAssassins attack Wayne Manor to try and kill Selina, causing her and Bruce to go on the run. While Harvey and Alfred try to find the kids, Gordon tries to track down the man he believes was behind the attack: Dick Lovecraft.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120502/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Rogues' Gallery", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nAn unknown person in Arkham Asylum is experimenting on the inmates, while Oswald unexpectedly finds himself in jail.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120506/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "What the Little Bird Told Him", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nIn an attempt to get his job back, Gordon seeks to capture Jack Gruber, a deranged electronics genius who has escaped from Arkham Asylum. Meanwhile, Falcone struggles to hold onto his empire after Fish Mooney makes her next move.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120512/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Welcome Back, Jim Gordon", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nWhen the key witness in a homicide ends up dead while being held for questioning by the police, Gordon suspects an inside job and looks to an old friend for information.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120516/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "The Fearsome Dr. Crane", episode_number: "S1, Ep14", description: "\nFish Mooney reveals a secret of Oswald Cobblepot's, prompting Maroni to take him on a trip to test his loyalty. Meanwhile, Gordon and Bullock hunt down a killer who targets victims with severe phobias and Bruce Wayne confronts Gordon for failing to make progress on his parents' murder case.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120520/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "The Scarecrow", episode_number: "S1, Ep15", description: "\nGordon and Bullock set out to stop Gerald Crane, a biology teacher who has been harvesting the glands of his murder victims. Meanwhile, after finding herself in an unusual setting, Mooney continues plotting to gain power, and Falcone attempts to change Maroni's plan for the Penguin. Then, Bruce takes a treacherous hike.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120524/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "The Blind Fortune Teller", episode_number: "S1, Ep16", description: "\nThe circus comes under attack while Gordon and Dr. Thompkins are in attendance.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120532/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Red Hood", episode_number: "S1, Ep17", description: "\nFollowing several bank robberies, Gordon and Bullock investigate the Red Hood gang. Meanwhile, Selina bonds with Barbara, Penguin faces problems, Fish tries to reclaim her position, and Alfred is visited by an old friend.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120538/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Everyone Has a Cobblepot", episode_number: "S1, Ep18", description: "\nWhile Gordon seeks information about the recent controversy with Commissioner Loeb, Fish's allegiance with the prisoners is questioned when she appears to join forces with Dr. Dulmacher. Meanwhile, after an attack close to home, Bruce deals with the aftermath.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120542/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Beasts of Prey", episode_number: "S1, Ep19", description: "\nGordon and Bullock inspect a cold case involving \"the Ogre\", a serial killer who targets young women in Gotham City. Meanwhile, Fish plots her escape from the Dollmaker, and Bruce and Selina confront Reggie.    ", season_id: 2431, series_id: 15, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4120544/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
