  {title: "Episode #1.1", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nIn Birmingham just after the Great War trenches veteran Thomas Shelby leads his gang, the Peaky Blinders, so named as they carry lethal razors in their peaked caps, who make money from illegal betting and the black market. Thomas, by mistake, appropriates a consignment of guns which have been stolen from the local arms factory and hard-nosed Inspector Campbell arrives from Ireland, charged by war minister Winston Churchill to recover it. Thomas's aunt Polly urges him to return it but he sees the opportunity to use it to his advantage. Thomas also quarrels with his ...    ", season_id: 2440, series_id: 18, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2471500/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Episode #1.2", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nThomas continues dating Grace, barmaid at the Garrison pub, unaware that she has been planted by Campbell to spy on his activities. At a country fair outside the city Thomas gets into a fight with the Lees, a violent family of travellers, who later send him a bullet with his name on, giving him another adversary to rank alongside Billy Kimber. Campbell sends a message to Thomas via Aunt Polly and they meet on neutral ground at a hotel. Thomas proposes to Campbell that if he leaves him alone he will return the guns. If he is arrested the guns will be sent to the IRA in...    ", season_id: 2440, series_id: 18, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2471502/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Episode #1.3", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nThomas is approached by two IRA members anxious to buy the guns, though he is careful not to commit himself. Grace, who has overheard, follows the Irishmen and ends up shooting one in self-defence though the IRA suspect the Peaky Blinders. Next day Thomas takes Grace to Cheltenham races, where he warns Kimber that the Lees are out to rob him. Arthur brings a gang who relieve the Lees of the money stolen as a result of which Kimber hires the Blinders as his security. He also tries to have his way with Grace but Thomas saves her by ungallantly claiming that she has ...    ", season_id: 2440, series_id: 18, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2471506/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Episode #1.4", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nThomas now has a legitimate betting licence and, although he is suspicious that she is not what she seems to be, employs Grace as his secretary. Younger brother John announces that, to give his children a mother, he is to marry again but Thomas disapproves of his choice of bride, prostitute Lizzie. Although the Lees attack and rob the Shelby house Thomas proposes a truce so that they can ally against Kimber. As part of the deal John marries the Lees' daughter Esme and Thomas sends word to Ada to attend the wedding. She is heavily pregnant and goes into labour at the ...    ", season_id: 2440, series_id: 18, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2461634/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Episode #1.5", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nPolly visits Ada with food for the baby but Ada, wrongly believing Thomas betrayed Freddie, will not see her. The reappearance of Arthur Senior, the Shelbys' father who deserted the family a decade earlier, also splits the family. Thomas rejects him but Arthur Junior is impressed by his tales of life in America and gives him money for a passage to the New World. Predictably the old man robs him. Another visitor is IRA leader Byrne, seeking to find out more about the fate of his cousin Ryan, the man killed by Grace. He demands the guns but Thomas sets a trap for Byrne ...    ", season_id: 2440, series_id: 18, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2461632/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Episode #1.6", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nPolly welcomes Ada and her baby back into the family as Peaky Blinders, led by Danny Whizz-Bang, also spring Freddie from jail. With the guns recovered Winston Churchill believes Grace should receive a commendation but Campbell has discovered that she has been with Thomas whilst Polly realizes her true identity and threatens her to leave Birmingham. Thomas gathers the Shelbys and Lees to take on Kimber's men but Kimber has got wind of the plan and leads his gangs into the Blinders' territory. A gun battle takes place and Kimber is killed. Thomas is now king of the ...    ", season_id: 2440, series_id: 18, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2461638/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "B.S.O.D.", episode_number: "S5, Ep1", description: "\nLionel is investigated in relation to Dominic's death. Away from Samaritan, Mr. Reese and Harold try to save the Machine. Root is on the run.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4677294/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "SNAFU", episode_number: "S5, Ep2", description: "\nRoot and Finch work on bringing Northern Lights back online. They are successful and thus they start receiving numbers from the irrelevant list. However, the Machine is not as productive as before.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679172/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Truth Be Told", episode_number: "S5, Ep3", description: "\nJay accidentally kills Manny's pet turtle and lies about it, Claire becomes jealous when Phil's ex-girlfriend pays a visit, and Mitchell makes a bold decision after he misses a family day because he's called in to work.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-03-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679178/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "6,741", episode_number: "S5, Ep4", description: "\nShaw escapes her captors, but the team is unsure of her mental state when she begins to act paranoid and reckless.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679198/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "ShotSeeker", episode_number: "S5, Ep5", description: "\nReese protects an NYPD analyst whose investigation into a software glitch has drawn the attention of Samaritan. Also, Reese and Fusco are threatened by an ally of Elias's, who is looking to avenge his friend's death.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679184/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "A More Perfect Union", episode_number: "S5, Ep6", description: "\nAlicia's case involving at-will employees trying to unionize sparks a possible mutiny at Lockhart Gardner. Meanwhile, Peter gives Alicia an opportunity to renew their wedding vows, but he also needs her help on the campaign.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679188/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "QSO", episode_number: "S5, Ep7", description: "\nRoot goes undercover at a radio station to protect the host of a conspiracy theory show who stumbles upon information that could get him killed. Also, Samaritan's agents try to convince a member of the team that their goals are noble.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679194/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Reassortment", episode_number: "S5, Ep8", description: "\nReese and Finch become trapped in a hospital that becomes ground zero for a deadly viral outbreak. Also, Samaritan's newest recruit has second thoughts and Shaw continues to struggle with reality.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679202/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Sotto Voce", episode_number: "S5, Ep9", description: "\nThe mysterious criminal mastermind known as \"The Voice\" returns and traps Reese and Fusco in their own precinct with several armed gang members and the latest POI. Also, Root makes a shocking discovery.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679200/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The Day the World Went Away", episode_number: "S5, Ep10", description: "\nFinch's number comes up when a fatal error blows his cover identity and sets off a deadly series of escalating encounters with Samaritan's operatives.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679206/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Synecdoche", episode_number: "S5, Ep11", description: "\nHarold goes on a road trip with the Machine, while the rest of the team receive a new number; the president of the United States.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-06-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679208/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: ".exe", episode_number: "S5, Ep12", description: "\nAs Reese and Shaw race to catch up with Finch, he infiltrates a maximum-security government facility in a desperate mission which could mean the end for not only Samaritan, but for himself and The Machine as well.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-06-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679212/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Return 0", episode_number: "S5, Ep13", description: "\nFinch, Reese, Fusco and Shaw embark on one last mission to prevent Samaritan from destroying The Machine and cementing its hold over mankind.    ", season_id: 2441, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-06-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4679214/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Panopticon", episode_number: "S4, Ep1", description: "\nRequired to assume new identities created by Root, the team tries to adapt to their new lives, but a new number complicates things.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3596112/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Nautilus", episode_number: "S4, Ep2", description: "\nHarold reluctantly agrees to help John protect a young woman who is participating in a dangerous and deadly game, meanwhile Shaw works with a group of thieves as her new cover identity.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3897378/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Wingman", episode_number: "S4, Ep3", description: "\nLucifer gets help from an unlikely source while trying to find the contents of his stolen container; Chloe uncovers a vital clue.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3915422/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Brotherhood", episode_number: "S4, Ep4", description: "\nThe next numbers the Machine provides are for fourteen-year-old Malcolm Booker, and his eight-year-old sister, Tracie Booker, who are in foster care as their mother is incarcerated on a conviction for illegal firearms possession. Reese, who is tasked with finding them, quickly learns that they are the intended targets, as they stole $500,000 in drug money from the Brotherhood, a gang led by the unknown Dominic. Reese knows of the Brotherhood because he helped put in jail one of the gang's higher ups, Link, who is now out. The DEA is interested in the case, their head ...    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3949562/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Prophets", episode_number: "S4, Ep5", description: "\nOn Election Day Reese shoots a potential jumper and is forced to go into counseling. The new number is for a pollster who suspects the election for Governor of New York was rigged. It was - by Samaritan, and his life is now in danger.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4062328/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Pretenders", episode_number: "S4, Ep6", description: "\nJohn and others try to prevent a fake detective from getting himself killed, while Harold attends a conference in Hong Kong.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4024758/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Honor Among Thieves", episode_number: "S4, Ep7", description: "\nShaw joins a team of international thieves in order to keep tabs on the latest POI, but an unexpected turn of events puts her in danger of being detected by Samaritan. Also, Finch and Root undertake a dangerous sabotage mission.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4069160/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Point of Origin", episode_number: "S4, Ep8", description: "\nReese volunteers as an NYPD police academy instructor in order to keep an eye on a talented young officer whose suspicious actions make him question her motives. Meanwhile, Martine, armed with information from Samaritan, hunts a member of the team.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4065456/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The Devil You Know", episode_number: "S4, Ep9", description: "\nReese must save Elias from the Brotherhood. He can't get any help from Root or Shaw since Shaw's cover is blown and Root is escorting her to underground.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4092950/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The Cold War", episode_number: "S4, Ep10", description: "\nSamaritan demonstrates its true power by taking control of New York for 48 hours and erasing crime from the city in an attempt to lure The Machine out of hiding.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-12-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4092956/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "If-Then-Else", episode_number: "S4, Ep11", description: "\nSamaritan launches a cyber-attack on the stock exchange, leaving the team with no choice but to embark on a possible suicide mission in a desperate attempt to stop a global economic catastrophe.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4128194/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Control-Alt-Delete", episode_number: "S4, Ep12", description: "\nControl is back and begins to question the methods and intentions of Samaritan. Also, alarming news reports of a pair of vigilantes rampaging through the Northeast begin to surface.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4159446/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "M.I.A.", episode_number: "S4, Ep13", description: "\nThe hunt for Shaw takes Root and Reese to a small town in upstate New York where not everything is as idyllic as it seems; Fusco and a former person of interest team up.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4157140/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Guilty", episode_number: "S4, Ep14", description: "\nWhile on a jury for a murder trial, Finch becomes suspicious of another juror; Reese starts to open up to a therapist.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4212498/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Q & A", episode_number: "S4, Ep15", description: "\nReese tries to protect a software programmer with a mysterious second life, but it's unclear which side of her life the threat is coming from. Meanwhile, Claire, a young hacker that Finch protected, reaches out to him for aid.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4251588/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Blunt", episode_number: "S4, Ep16", description: "\nReese and Finch must protect a street-smart grifter after her plan to steal cash from a medical marijuana dispensary fails.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4334116/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Karma", episode_number: "S4, Ep17", description: "\nReese and Finch try to protect a psychologist whose unorthodox methods for helping his patients find closure could cost him dearly. Meanwhile, flashbacks reveal Finch fragile state in days following bombing that killed his best friend, Nathan Ingram.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4364356/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Skip", episode_number: "S4, Ep18", description: "\nReese must protect a bounty hunter who refuses to let the potential threat to her life deter her from the relentless pursuit of her target. Also, Finch tries to set the plan he began in Shanghai in motion.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4454364/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Search and Destroy", episode_number: "S4, Ep19", description: "\nReese and Finch scramble to protect a software CEO when his behavior becomes erratic following a hacker attack that reveals all his secrets and unravels his life.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4460310/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Terra Incognita", episode_number: "S4, Ep20", description: "\nReese tries to honor Carter's memory by solving a cold case she was unable to.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4460312/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Asylum", episode_number: "S4, Ep21", description: "\nReese and Fusco get caught in the war between Elias and Dominic while Finch and Root follow a clue to Shaw's whereabouts.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4540234/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "YHWH", episode_number: "S4, Ep22", description: "\nFinch and Root race to save The Machine, which has been located by the rival AI, Samaritan.    ", season_id: 2442, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-05-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4532988/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Liberty", episode_number: "S3, Ep1", description: "\nNobody knows where the Machine has now relocated itself, but it is still in contact with both Finch and, by association, Reese and their new partner Shaw, as well as Root. Still institutionalized, Root may have a short term problem in dealing with her psychiatrist, whom she sees as being stupid, and from whom she has not been provided access to any electronic devices including telephones. Carter, now demoted to patrol following her HR-initiated wrongful shooting incident, has her own new primary agenda. She has also not told Finch or Reese of her association with a ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-09-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2911556/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Nothing to Hide", episode_number: "S3, Ep2", description: "\nThe next number the machine dispenses is for Wayne Kruger, an Internet genius and head of a company called Life Trace, which allows people to find others through information readily available already on the web. However, Finch learns that Life Trace's primary goal, its money making venture, is as a data broker, selling the information it gathers to people who will pay for it. As Kruger prepares to make what is perhaps the biggest deal of his career, he wants to be as open and transparent as possible with his prospective clients... or so he says. Finch, Reese and Shaw ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3092846/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Lady Killer", episode_number: "S3, Ep3", description: "\nThe next number the machine dispenses is for Ian Murphy, a young man who lives off his investments. Years earlier he was a struggling college student who inherited $100,000 which he now has in a diverse portfolio of investments. Reese and Shaw initially follow him on a date. While Reese decides to check out his apartment, Shaw continues her tail. What they both find leads them to believe that Murphy is the perpetrator, stalking then killing the long list of women he meets through online means and of whom he has been keeping detailed dossiers. There is at least one ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3146366/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Reasonable Doubt", episode_number: "S3, Ep4", description: "\nA famous television producer is accused by his ex-wife of molesting their daughter, but is she just trying to get revenge for leaving her for her younger sister?    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3106152/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Razgovor", episode_number: "S3, Ep5", description: "\nShaw is tasked to stay close to a 10-year-old identified by The Machine, who is wanted by the Russians. Meanwhile, Carter's mission to bring HR to justice risks exposure.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3146370/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Mors Praematura", episode_number: "S3, Ep6", description: "\nReese and Finch go on separate missions. Finch has noticed that Shaw has been less responsive than she even usually is and he sends Reese to go find her. Reese initially discovers evidence that Shaw was abducted, but later finds more evidence that she may have gone willingly with her abductor: Root. He has to find what Root is up to, she who has been in contact with the Machine, which is feeding her information for her latest mission requiring Shaw's assistance. In the meantime, Finch works on their latest number, that of Timothy Sloan, an estate investigator for the ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3146372/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "The Perfect Mark", episode_number: "S3, Ep7", description: "\nWhile Finch still keeps Root hostage, he who can't understand why the Machine is in contact with her, he is the first to make contact with their latest number, that of hypnotherapist Hayden Price. The fact that his credentials seem made up, and that the therapy session in which Finch has with him seems more like a fishing exercise to obtain answers to secret website questions, lead Finch to quickly come to the conclusion that Price is a con man, out to bilk his patients. However, he still believes that Price is the intended target. In following Price's world, Reese, ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3210020/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Endgame", episode_number: "S3, Ep8", description: "\nAs Ava Hessington's murder trial begins. Harvey, Mike and Jessica fight off betrayal from both inside the firm and out. Meanwhile, Louis and Donna seek to even the score with those who have done them wrong.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-09-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3227888/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The Crossing", episode_number: "S3, Ep9", description: "\nAs a favor to the D.A. in Boston, Hotchner and Rossi profile a woman who murdered her husband, though the D.A. may not like their findings. Back at the office, J.J.'s personalization of a stalker case baffles the rest of the team.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2008-05-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3291628/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The Devil's Share", episode_number: "S3, Ep10", description: "\nThe team seeks justice for Carter's murder, but Finch realizes that one person may go too far in the battle against HR. Meanwhile, NYPD officer Patrick Simmons' number comes up.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3331452/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Lethe", episode_number: "S3, Ep11", description: "\nFlashbacks to Finch's adolescence provide insight into his creation of The Machine. Also, the team receives the number of an already dying man, and Reese leaves the POI team behind in the aftermath of the war with the crime organization.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-12-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3331420/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Aletheia", episode_number: "S3, Ep12", description: "\nFinch, Shaw and Arthur Claypool are able to escape from the clutches of Control, after which Arthur demonstrates that he has more lucid moments than he initially lets on. He informs Finch and Shaw more about Samaritan, and what from that project still exists, which is what Control was after. As the threesome try to protect Samaritan, they are tracked both by Control's team, led by Hersh, and Vigilance, led by Collier. Control has other issues on her mind, namely dealing with Root, who tries fruitlessly to explain to Control her relationship with the Machine, which ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3331424/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "4C", episode_number: "S3, Ep13", description: "\nUnder the assumed name John Wiley, Reese is making his escape from his life with Finch and the Machine by taking a one-way flight to Istanbul. He is however diverted onto another flight via Rome. Initially believing it is all Finch's doing, Reese soon learns that he was placed onto that Rome flight by the Machine, who provides him with the next number in the form of a seat number on the plane. \"4C\" is occupied by a young man named Owen Matthews, who is accompanied by who Reese recognizes as two federal marshals. Reese initially has no intention about doing anything ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3364202/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Provenance", episode_number: "S3, Ep14", description: "\nReese rejoins Finch in New York, but when the team receives the number of a highly skilled antiquities thief, a surprising turn of events finds them planning a heist which could land them all in jail.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3364208/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Last Call", episode_number: "S3, Ep15", description: "\nThe death of a bar owner takes Castle and Beckett back in time to the prohibition era.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-12-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3377942/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "RAM", episode_number: "S3, Ep16", description: "\nA flashback to the early days of Finch's operations reveals secrets and connections with far-reaching implications.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3547404/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "/", episode_number: "S3, Ep17", description: "\nThe Machine tasks Root to find a janitor who has a mysterious past. However, when her presence endangers him, the Machine sends his number to Finch as well.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3520032/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Allegiance", episode_number: "S3, Ep18", description: "\nThe team gets involved in a case of international politics when a former government contractor stalks a U.N. diplomat. Meanwhile, an adversary tries to take advantage of Root.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3526628/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Most Likely to...", episode_number: "S3, Ep19", description: "\nReese, Shaw and Finch are too late for their latest number, Leona Wainwright, as she is killed in front of Reese and Shaw's eyes. They know that Leona was killed by Vigilance for information she would have had unwittingly with regard to the Machine as a federal government employee. Finch decides to take Fusco to Washington DC to see if they can discover what information Vigilance wants, which is probably housed somewhere in Leona's physical or virtual office. Their problem is that the FBI is also involved in the investigation, which means that the Bureau has first ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3614882/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Death Benefit", episode_number: "S3, Ep20", description: "\nNews of Northern Lights has hit the media, meaning that the team's work has become more difficult if only because of the public eye on what is happening. While Shaw heads off with Root on her next assignment, Reese heads to Washington DC to reunite with Finch for their next number, that belonging to Illinois Congressman Roger McCourt. Finch's initial guess is that they are heading into uncharted territory as he believes that McCourt is not only the target or the perpetrator of an individual crime, but also that his number is related to terrorism or national security ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3615622/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Beta", episode_number: "S3, Ep21", description: "\nDecima hunts down Reese and Shaw using Samaritan's feeds. Meanwhile, Greer sets a trap for Finch by targeting his former fiancée, Grace.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3615624/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "A House Divided", episode_number: "S3, Ep22", description: "\nDecima has completed its beta test of Samaritan and has now shut it down temporarily as Greer has to get the politicos, namely Garrison, to buy into the need to purchase it in the name of national security. Greer needs this to happen as they require the government feeds for Samaritan to operate properly. With Finch now being held by Greer and Decima, Reese believes that their first priority should be to retrieve him. However, Root, in her continuing contact with the Machine, convinces Reese and Shaw that the Machine is telling her that Finch, for the time being, is ...    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3615628/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Deus Ex Machina", episode_number: "S3, Ep23", description: "\nThe team takes desperate action in its race to prevent Samaritan from coming online and making them its first targets. Meanwhile, the months-long battle with the anti-surveillance terrorist group Vigilance comes to a shocking conclusion.    ", season_id: 2443, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3615630/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "The Contingency", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nMr. Reese breaks Finch's code of communicating with the Machine in order to save the new number, Leon, who stole money from some Aryan outlaws. He then convinces the Machine to help him find Finch.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-09-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2255900/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Bad Code", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nDetective Carter and Mr. Reese go to Texas to look into Root's past. Root shows to Finch that the people who bought his Machine are evil. Mr. Reese finally finds Finch.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-10-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2341524/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Masquerade", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nKatherine becomes a threat to Mystic Falls and Stefan and Damon decide to stop her at the Lockwood's masquerade ball. Bonnie, Jeremy, Alaric and Caroline help the Salvatore brothers but Katherine brings the witch Lucy to protect her. Meanwhile Matt picks fight with Tyler, but Caroline hits Matt avoiding the fight. Sarah is also compelled by Katherine to pick a fight with Tyler if Matt fails.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-10-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2341526/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Triggerman", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nMr. Reese and Finch try to protect a man involved in organized crime that has a bounty on him.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-10-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2341532/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Bury the Lede", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nThe FBI are getting closer to the head of HR. Mr. Reese tries to prevent a young journalist that likes taking risks from being killed. To avoid getting media attention, Mr. Reese starts dating her. Fusco is playing double.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-11-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2341536/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The High Road", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nJohn and Zoe go deep undercover as husband and wife to get close to a person who's been using a dead guy's identity for the past 15 years.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-11-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2368860/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Critical", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nLeon is trapped for his own protection. A medical doctor faces a difficult decision. Detective Carter encounters agent Snow.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-11-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2384950/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Til Death", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nMr. Reese and Mr. Finch try to stop a rich married couple from killing each other.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-11-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2484360/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "C.O.D.", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nFinch and Mr. Reese try to protect a taxi driver that is being chased by the Estonian mafia. HR try to make a deal with Elias.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-12-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2484372/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Shadow Box", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nReese and Finch's latest number is twenty-six year old Abby Monroe, who they expect will be the target based on basic information they have about her. She is a past honor student having received a degree in engineering. She worked the past year for Homes for Our Returning Heroes, a military charity that supports returning veterans financially, that job Reese and Finch surmise in honor of her brother who was killed in Afghanistan. She, however, left that job to work instead for the city planning department. Their belief that she will be the target does not diminish ...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-12-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2532054/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "2 Pi R", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nSpecial Agent Donnelly has Reese, along with three other men, in seventy-two hour custody on Riker's Island. With Finch's help, Carter is in unofficial charge of helping Reese get out of custody without disclosing to Donnelly that Reese is indeed the \"man in the suit\" that Donnelly considers the most dangerous man on the loose. Although Carter has a plan to do so, she may find that tenacious Donnelly may not let Reese and the other three go so easily if he has not yet found out which one is the man in the suit. Meanwhile, Finch, largely with Fusco's help, is handling ...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2558980/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Prisoner's Dilemma", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nFinch and Carter are trying to get Reese out of Riker's, where he is still being kept prisoner by Donnelly. Meanwhile, Fusco is working alone in the next number.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2562802/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Dead Reckoning", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nAs Donnelly escorts Carter and Reese to their incarceration, they are ambushed, their attacker who kills Donnelly and abducts Reese. That attacker is Reese's old and supposedly deceased ex-partner, Kara Stanton. Reese is not the first old colleague who she has abducted, the other being their old boss, Mark Snow. She has bombs strapped to their chests, and places them on a collective task, which she monitors remotely, and threatens to blow them up if they don't comply. They have to figure out her motives to uncover what her mission is. Meanwhile, Donnelly's death ...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2562804/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "One Percent", episode_number: "S2, Ep14", description: "\nThe next number Reese and Finch work on is that of Logan Pierce, a self-made billionaire, whose social networking website, friendczar.com, which he founded and still operates with his best friend and partner, Justin Ogilvie, is going public in 72 hours. This IPO has the potential to be the largest in history. Reese and Finch believe Pierce is the intended target as his reckless and win-at-all-cost mentality has resulted in him making many enemies. These potential enemies include competitors, all of whom friendczar has crushed many in immoral ways, and his own company ...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2562806/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Booked Solid", episode_number: "S2, Ep15", description: "\nReese and Finch get jobs as a bellhop and concierge respectively at the upscale, 700 guest Coronet Hotel where the next number, Mira Dobrica, works as a maid. They figure that whatever will happen by or to Mira will happen at the hotel since she works 60 hour weeks there. Mira is a streetwise woman, who arrived in the US in 1999 as a refugee from the war in Kosovo. Reese and Finch believe she will be the target. Figuring out who the perpetrator is will be difficult as the 700 guests are primarily unknown. After their initial stint at the hotel, they believe the case ...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2613404/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Relevance", episode_number: "S2, Ep16", description: "\nSam Shaw and her associate Michael Cole recieve the relevant numbers from the machine, but Reese and Finch must help them, before is too late.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2646630/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Proteus", episode_number: "S2, Ep17", description: "\nCoinciding with a storm hitting the eastern tri-state area which may require evacuation of coastal residents, the machine has not provided any numbers in three days, leading Reese and Finch to believe that there might be something wrong with it, especially what Stanton may have done to it prior to her death. When the machine does provide a number, it provides six men simultaneously, five who are officially missing or have ceased their electronic footprint. Reese and Finch decide to focus on the sixth, Jack Rollins - Finch at his New York apartment, Reese at his rented...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-03-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2725454/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "All In", episode_number: "S2, Ep18", description: "\nHolmes and Watson investigate a burglary at an illegal high stakes poker game held by Mycroft's ex girlfriend. Watson is suspicious of their employer.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2721856/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Trojan Horse", episode_number: "S2, Ep19", description: "\nThe next number the machine dispenses is for Monica Jacobs, a senior vice-president with Rylatech, a computer networking firm. Monica is highly regarded as a rising star in the business. She is seemingly fiercely loyal to the company, which was built from nothing by its now wealthy owner, Martin Baxter. Because of the nature of the business, Finch is more qualified than Reese to go undercover within the highly secured company. Finch sees what he believes is corporate espionage on Monica's part, but learns that she has uncovered information about the death of a junior ...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2757448/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "In Extremis", episode_number: "S2, Ep20", description: "\nReese first catches up with the latest number, Dr. Richard Nelson, when he is being awarded the title of professor emeritus at a lavish dinner banquet. Dr. Nelson is a well respected and renowned cardiac surgeon and researcher, with his credentials suggesting that he is the target. That is indeed the case, but Reese and Finch are too late: someone has poisoned Dr. Nelson after he ingested something at that banquet that was slipped into his food or drink. Dr. Nelson first believes that Reese is the culprit, but Reese convinces him that he is only there to help find who...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2734238/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Zero Day", episode_number: "S2, Ep21", description: "\nIt's been ten days since the machine has provided a number, which means Carter has had ten days of dead bodies piling up. Finch discovers that a company called Decima is responsible for the virus which is causing these problems of inconsistency. The machine finally does dispense a number, it belonging to Ernest Thornhill, whose business of late has been buying up pay phone companies. As Finch and Reese track Thornhill, who they have yet actually to see, they find out some important information about him and exactly why the machine dispensed his number. But also aware ...    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-05-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2832794/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "God Mode", episode_number: "S2, Ep22", description: "\nReese and Finch team up with surprising allies in a race to save The Machine from Root and the mysterious international organization, Decima, who have both re-emerged with dangerous agendas.    ", season_id: 2444, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-05-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2832792/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Pilot", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nWhen the social security number of a young prosecutor comes up, Reese and Finch work together to figure out if their person of interest is the victim or perpetrator.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-09-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1941917/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Ghosts", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nA woman found drowned in a bathtub full of motor oil is initially identified as a missing suburban housewife, until it's discovered that her identity had been stolen from a deceased child, and that she had been a fugitive from a terrorism charge for two decades.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-04-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2007219/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Mission Creep", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nThe latest number is an ex-soldier who's now part of a gang that specialize in robberies. Mr. Reese goes undercover, infiltrating the gang. This triggers memories of Jessica.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-10-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2013850/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Cura Te Ipsum", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nReese and Finch surveil their latest POI, Dr. Megan Tillman, while she's on call and after hours to unravel the threat surrounding the promising young physician.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-10-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2033779/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Judgement", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nWhen the Machine produces the social security number of a judge renowned for his tough sentencing, Reese and Finch have the added challenge of investigating a POI who wants nothing to do with their brand of vigilante justice.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-10-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2043518/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The Fix", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nMr. Reese goes as the new driver of fixer Zoe Morgan in order to decide if she's a victim or perpetrator. When Zoe listens to a recording she isn't supposed to, she becomes the target of a pharmaceutical company.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-10-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2051590/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Witness", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nA potential witness in a rape case is reluctant to testify because she is an illegal immigrant who both witnessed and was the victim of unspeakable war crimes against women in the Democratic Republic of the Congo.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-03-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2069479/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Foe", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nWhen Reese and Finch discover that their latest POI has connections to Cold War Soviet espionage circles, they quickly learn how covert ops were handled in a world before The Machine.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-11-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2078287/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Get Carter", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nReese and Finch's game of cat and mouse with Detective Carter becomes infinitely more complicated when The Machine declares that she is their newest POI.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-12-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2089317/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Number Crunch", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nAs Detective Carter deals with the fallout from her recent encounter with Reese and Finch, The Machine ups the ante for the duo by giving them four Social Security numbers instead of one.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-12-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2101550/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Super", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nReese works the computer while Finch does the legwork with their latest POI, a building super who keeps too close an eye on his tenants. Meanwhile, Detective Carter may finally get her long-awaited glimpse into a case.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-01-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2110973/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Legacy", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nWhen Carter finally comes face-to-face with Reese, he urges her to join forces to help with their latest POI, a scrappy young woman from the wrong side of the tracks who turned her life around and became a lawyer.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-01-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2131933/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Root Cause", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nFinch and Reese run surveillance on a man who's been unemployed for eight months without his family knowing. Angry that he's been fired, he may pose a threat to society.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-02-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2181307/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Wolf and Cub", episode_number: "S1, Ep14", description: "\nThe Machine identifies Darren, a teenager whose brother was just murdered, as the next POI. Meanwhile, Finch is growing concerned that the son of his former business partner is dangerously close to finding out about The Machine.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-02-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2178549/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Blue Code", episode_number: "S1, Ep15", description: "\nReese discovers there's more to the story after he infiltrates a smuggling ring to get close to his latest POI.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-02-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2197079/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Risk", episode_number: "S1, Ep16", description: "\nThe Machine leads Reese and Finch to Wall Street when a sharp young trader at a major investment bank becomes embroiled in a multi-million dollar financial scam.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-02-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2223063/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Baby Blue", episode_number: "S1, Ep17", description: "\nWhen Moretti gets released from prison, Carter and Mr. Reese team up to protect him from Elias. Meanwhile, Finch's new number is an eight-months old baby girl, whose mother has just been murdered.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-03-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2225373/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Identity Crisis", episode_number: "S1, Ep18", description: "\nHarvey and Louis come to blows after Louis' reckless behavior threatens to cost the firm a case, while Mike is assigned to a businessman who is trying to get back money from his estranged daughter.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-08-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2239935/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Flesh and Blood", episode_number: "S1, Ep19", description: "\nA Saudi Arabian limo driver dies in an explosion of a car aboard NAS Patuxent River; Gibbs and company investigate; the apparent target is a Saudi prince present there for advanced training. The gang figure it out. Tony's father visits.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-01-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2270357/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Matsya Nyaya", episode_number: "S1, Ep20", description: "\nIn 2012, Mr. Reese goes undercover as a security guard to prevent a robbery. In 2010, CIA plan to eliminate two of their best agents.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-04-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2289155/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Many Happy Returns", episode_number: "S1, Ep21", description: "\nFinch gives Mr. Reese the day off as it's his birthday and chooses to work the new number with Fusco. FBI start looking into the murder of Jessica's husband.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-05-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2319363/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "No Good Deed", episode_number: "S1, Ep22", description: "\nDiNozzo is partnered with his girlfriend, ATF Special Agent Zoë Keates, after evidence reveals that the murder weapon in an NCIS case was originally purchased for the controversial ATF sting, \"Operation Fast and Furious.\" Also, Anthony DiNozzo Sr. returns to town for a special dinner to meet his son's girlfriend.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2330007/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Firewall", episode_number: "S1, Ep23", description: "\nReese is trapped next to a person of interest in a part of the city extremely controlled and needs the help of Finch, Fusco and Carter.    ", season_id: 2445, series_id: 19, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-05-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2380789/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
