  {title: "Pilot, Part 1", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nTime-traveling rogue, Rip Hunter, has to recruit a rag-tag team of heroes and villains to help prevent an apocalypse that could impact not only Earth, but all of time.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4566516/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Pilot, Part 2", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nThe team meet Vandal Savage, who senses the presence of Hawkman and Hawkgirl. A fight follows in which Ray loses a piece of his costume that threatens to change the future. Then the team plan to correct that.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4743844/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Blood Ties", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nRip decides to weaken Vandal Savage by going after his financial assets. Rip and Sara infiltrate Savage's bank, but are discovered by his men. Meanwhile Snart and Rory talk Jax into taking the Waverider back to Central City so they can steal a valuable emerald. Professor Stein guides Ray on a dangerous mission.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4832610/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "White Knights", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nDr. Stein sneaks into a lab and finds out that Savage is trying to create Firestorm.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4838236/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Fail-Safe", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nAfter some of the Legends are captured and thrown into a Russian gulag during the height of the Cold War of 1986, Snart leads the team in an elaborate Prison Break to free their comrades. However, Rip gives Sara a secret side mission that could prove not only to be a liability, but fatal to the team.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4845364/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Star City 2046", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nA malfunction sends the Waverider to 2046 Star City where the team faces a future in which they fail to stop Savage and return home.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4857194/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Marooned", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nWhen there's no trace of Savage, Rip spends time dwelling on the past and Rory continues to be a liability to the team. The crew receive a distress call from another Time Master and seek it out, only to find that the ship was commandeered by time pirates. Snart has an important decision to make.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4871756/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Night of the Hawk", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nThe team tracks Savage to a small town in Oregon in the 1950s where they suspect he's involved in a recent string of murders.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4877414/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Left Behind", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nRay, Sara and Kendra are stranded in the '50s when the Waverider takes off without them.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4899930/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Progeny", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nThe team is divided over killing a 14-year-old boy who will grow to be a powerful ally for Savage.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4932662/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "The Magnificent Eight", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nThe Legends travel back to the Old Wild West and gain the aid of a true legend - a morally ambiguous gunslinger with a penchant for danger named Jonah Hex.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4949298/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Last Refuge", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nA deadly assassin called the Pilgrim wants to wipe the Legends from the timeline by killing the heroes' younger selves before they become powerful.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4952750/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Leviathan", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nRip takes the team to London in the year 2166, three days before his family is killed. He believes this to be their final opportunity to take out Savage who is, unfortunately, at the height of his power. However, the team discovers two key elements to defeating him - Savage's daughter and the means to kill Savage once and for all.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4952746/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "River of Time", episode_number: "S1, Ep14", description: "\nAfter numerous attempts in many different time periods, the team has successfully captured Vandal Savage. However, Savage tells Kendra that he can reunite her with Carter so she struggles with whether she should kill him. Rip decides they will deliver Savage to the Time Masters which doesn't sit well with Snart and Rory. The duo decides it may be time to jump ship and return to their old life. Meanwhile, Savage taunts Ray about his place in Kendra's life.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4952748/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Destiny", episode_number: "S1, Ep15", description: "\nBeing in the vicinity of the Time Masters leaves Rip and Rory incredibly disturbed for very different reasons. Meanwhile, Sara takes over the Waverider, Kendra is reunited with Carter and Snart decides he might be a hero after all.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4952752/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Legendary", episode_number: "S1, Ep16", description: "\nAfter the numerous sacrifices the team has made since the beginning of this ride, Rip decides that it's time they each decide their own destiny and returns them to Central City a few months after they first left. Returned to their normal lives, each team member must individually decide if they are willing to sacrifice everything in order to save the world. Meanwhile, Sara visits with her father who delivers some heartbreaking news about her sister.    ", season_id: 2459, series_id: 22, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5052438/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Live Free or Die", episode_number: "S5, Ep1", description: "\nNow that Gus is dead, Walt, Jesse, and Mike work to cover their tracks. Skyler panics when Ted Beneke wakes up.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-07-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2081647/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Madrigal", episode_number: "S5, Ep2", description: "\nWalt and Jesse pursue an unlikely business partner; the DEA follows new leads.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-07-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301457/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Hazard Pay", episode_number: "S5, Ep3", description: "\nThe guys put a business plan into action; Walt confesses to Marie.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-07-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301459/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Fifty-One", episode_number: "S5, Ep4", description: "\nIt's Walt's 51st birthday. His return to the drug business causes Skyler to go into depression.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-08-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301461/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Dead Freight", episode_number: "S5, Ep5", description: "\nThe boys plan on robbing a train that has an entire car of methylamine.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-08-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301463/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Buyout", episode_number: "S5, Ep6", description: "\nWalt, Jesse and Mike distress over the future of their business; occupational hazards weigh heavily on Jesse.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-08-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301465/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Say My Name", episode_number: "S5, Ep7", description: "\nMike and Jesse are out. Now Walt has to handle things on his own. Hank finally finds a rat in Mike's gang.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-08-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301467/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Gliding Over All", episode_number: "S5, Ep8", description: "\nWalt expands his business overseas, and the money is pouring in.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-09-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301469/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Blood Money", episode_number: "S5, Ep9", description: "\nWalt is out of the meth business and trying to move on with his life. Jesse tries to get rid of his money. Hank now knows that Walt is the famous Heisenberg.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-08-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301471/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Buried", episode_number: "S5, Ep10", description: "\nHank is determined to bring down Walt. Walt scrambles to hide evidence before Hank gets to it, and Skyler tries to stop Hank and Marie from taking away the kids.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-08-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301443/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Confessions", episode_number: "S5, Ep11", description: "\nWalt makes his next move against Hank, putting Hank in a tough position. Hank confronts Jesse and attempts to turn him against Walt, and Jesse decides it's time to move on. Meanwhile, Todd has taken over the business.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-08-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301445/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Rabid Dog", episode_number: "S5, Ep12", description: "\nWalt discovers Jesse broke into his house and attempted to burn it down. Walt wants to protect his family so he moves them into a hotel for a few nights. Jesse makes plans to take down Walt.    ", season_id: 2460, series_id: 23, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-09-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2301447/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
