  {title: "We Were All Someone Else Yesterday", episode_number: "S3, Ep6", description: "\nHood copes with Siobhan's death. The FBI takes over in the hunt for Chayton. A wedge is driven between Proctor and Rebecca.    ", season_id: 2466, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3860506/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "You Can't Hide from the Dead", episode_number: "S3, Ep7", description: "\nChayton receives aid from an unexpected source. Gordon and Carrie break Deva out of a party. The night of the heist on Stowe's base arrives, but Hood's hallucinations with Kelly might put the plan at risk.    ", season_id: 2466, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3908124/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "All the Wisdom I Got Left", episode_number: "S3, Ep8", description: "\nHood and Brock track down Chayton to Louisiana. Rebecca makes new enemies for her uncle. Colonel Stowe prepares his revenge for the robbery at the base.    ", season_id: 2466, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3908126/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Even God Doesn't Know What to Make of You", episode_number: "S3, Ep9", description: "\nProctor is captured and tortured. Gordon makes a difficult decision about Deva. Bunker goes after his former gang. Job, Sugar and Carrie are taken by Stowe and his mercenaries.    ", season_id: 2466, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4086612/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "We All Pay Eventually", episode_number: "S3, Ep10", description: "\nHood joins forces with Gordon to save his friends from Stowe. Meanwhile, Proctor heads to Philadelphia to settle the score with Frazier, as Bunker is set on his personal revenge against his brother.    ", season_id: 2466, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4086614/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Little Fish", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nThe fallout from the rescue of Sheriff Lucas is at hand. Special Agent Racine is in town to investigate. He holds a hearing for all involved. Carrie is not allowed to see her children. Job, Lucas, Sugar, and Carrie rob an armored truck.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2813706/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The Thunder Man", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nCarrie Hopewell has her trial. She is sentenced to 30 days in prison. DA Hopewell does nothing to help. Tensions between the Longshadow's and Proctor's intensify. Deputy Kelly's abusive ex-husband returns to town with extreme consequences.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2813708/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "The Warrior Class", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nA young Kinaho girl is murdered on Amish land. She was seeing Soloman, the little brother of Rebecca. Hostilities ensue between the Kinaho and the Amish. Proctor comes to the aid of his people. Hood has a surprising visitor from his past.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2861116/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Bloodlines", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nLucas questions an Amish teacher who is known to be violent and somewhat radical. Chayton attempts an escape while being transported. Proctor uses his special brand of magic to find his nephew. Nola delivers final justice for Lana Cleary.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2928310/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "The Truth About Unicorns", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nCarrie is let out of prison. Lucas is waiting on her. They take a detour to the house they talked about so long ago. They are not alone in their dream. Someone has followed them there. Is it Rabbit? Is it Gordon? Is it Agent Racine?    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2928336/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Armies of One", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nGordon and Deva find that they need Carrie in their lives and Rebecca receives a lesson in loyalty from proctor. Meanwhile, Lucas Jason's past catches up with him.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2928312/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Ways to Bury a Man", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nHood goes after Proctor with a vengeance after he discovers that Proctor was behind Jason's death. Max has a severe asthma attack. Gordon and Carrie discuss their options. Alex Longshadow faces a no-confidence vote by the Tribal Council.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2928338/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Evil for Evil", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nJob gets a lead on the whereabouts of Rabbit. Lucas arrests Proctor, but is the cost worth it? The skinheads look for payback against Emmett for that beat-down he gave them previously. Carrie gets the money for Max's treatment.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2928324/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Homecoming", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nThe homecoming dance becomes the backdrop for a battle of lethal wits between Damon's party, including Mikael and Rebeka although not at all reconciled, and Klaus's, which fields the hybrids by diverting the party to the Lockwood mansion. Tyler surprises Caroline by stating he doesn't really mind being under Klaus's spell as hybrid, it's not worse then monthly lunatic agony as pure werewolf. Fearing even with the eternal oak stake in Mikael's hand Klaus may outsmart them, Damon secretly enlisted Katherine, but Klaus prepared the most stunning surprise.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-11-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3053838/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Bullets and Tears", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nProctor gets out of jail. With Juliet gone and Alex visiting the slaughter house in his absence, Rebecca's allegiance is in question. Lucas and Carrie use memories of the past to fortify themselves for the battle with a merciless Rabbit.    ", season_id: 2467, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3053842/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Pilot", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nAfter completing his 15 year prison sentence, an ex-con tracks down his former partner, now known as Carrie Hopewell, in Banshee County Pennsylvania who it turns out is now married to the local DA and has two children. He takes her at her word when she says she doesn't have any of the cash they stole. Later at a roadside bar, he meets the county's new Sheriff, Lucas Hood who has literally just arrived in town and has yet to meet anyone. When Hood is killed during an attempted robbery, the ex-con assumes his identity. The town's youthful mayor wanted to bring in an ...    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2313681/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The Rave", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nKai Proctor begins the process of co-opting Sheriff Hood but Lucas isn't biting. Lucas continues to build his cover and Job confirms that the real Lucas Hood has few friends or relatives who may blow his cover. Siobhan Kelly realizes that Lucas seems to know little about police procedures. Carrie Hopewell's daughter Deva is definitely getting in with the wrong crowd. Hanson has organized a rave in a vacant barn without Proctor's knowledge. The police raid the rave - the sole purpose of which is to sell drugs to teenagers - but Lucas' approach to shutting it down is ...    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2169286/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Meet the New Boss", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nAnastasia breaks into her father's extremely secure home to make a deal for her safety. Proctor and Longshadow make a deal to build a hotel on the reservation. Hood performs his brand of an arrest on a rapist, ultimate fighter champion.    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2272320/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Half Deaf Is Better Than All Dead", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nLucas sets off an alarm while trying to steal a painting from the Harrisburg State Museum. He contacts Job to help him break out. After getting video proof that Proctor killed Hanson, Lucas arrests him. However, the Moody's get in the way.    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2392675/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "The Kindred", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nA motorcycle gang invades Banshee. They attack Carrie and Sugar at the town Spirit Festival. The killing of one of the bikers by Deputy Kelly during the attack triggers a chain of violent events.    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2198566/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Wicks", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nAn ex-prison mate friend of Sheriff Hood named Wicks shows up unexpectedly in Banshee. Wicks causes Hood to remember all the pain and torment he went through in prison. Proctor blackmails the local Reverend to sale his house.    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2272322/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Behold a Pale Rider", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nAna makes arrangements to kidnap Hood and leave him for Rabbit to find. A drugstore hold-up turns into a hostage situation at the local high school. Job frees Lucas in time for him to save the students in the school, including Deva.    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2371798/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "We Shall Live Forever", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nOlek finds Ana and Hood in Banshee. The ensuing showdown results in dire consequences. George seeks answers for Carrie's behavior. Rebecca is shunned by the Amish. Proctor pleads with his aunt and father to take her back.    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-03-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2356588/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Always the Cowboy", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nHood rushes Ana to the hospital after finding her badly beaten and suffering. Rabbit comes to Banshee. An injured and distraught Ana rushes to find her children. However, she is too late to prevent Rabbit from kidnapping Max.    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-03-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2372062/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "A Mixture of Madness", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nRabbit sends a hit squad after Lucas. He is saved by an unlikely ally. Lucas makes a decision that will have dramatic consequences on many people in Banshee. Job, Carrie, Sugar and the three deputies go after Lucas.    ", season_id: 2468, series_id: 24, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-03-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2403698/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Episode #5.1", episode_number: "S5, Ep1", description: "\n  Add a Plot\n    ", season_id: 2469, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2017-02-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5419058/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Chapter 40", episode_number: "S4, Ep1", description: "\nClare's absence causes problems for Frank on the campaign trail amid rumors of a marital rift. Claire tries to strike out on her own.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4498368/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Chapter 41", episode_number: "S4, Ep2", description: "\nAs Claire begins exploring a campaign of her own, she and Frank engage in backdoor political maneuvering. But this time they're not on the same side.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4817660/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Chapter 42", episode_number: "S4, Ep3", description: "\nClaire joins Frank as he campaigns in South Carolina, but he doesn't trust her. A disastrous scandal blindsides Frank on primary day.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4817664/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Chapter 43", episode_number: "S4, Ep4", description: "\nClaire threatens Frank while Frank makes a politically bold move that may provoke Russia.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4817670/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Chapter 44", episode_number: "S4, Ep5", description: "\nClaire advises the VP Donald Blythe on dealing with Russia. Further investigation of Lucas Goodwin dredges up his accusations against Frank.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4949018/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Chapter 45", episode_number: "S4, Ep6", description: "\nClaire clashes with the Secretary of State Durant over her involvement in negotiations with Russia. Dunbar must choose between her campaign and her ethics.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4949028/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Chapter 46", episode_number: "S4, Ep7", description: "\nFrank and Claire adjust to their new reality. The search for Frank's running mate begins. Frank starts a campaign to weaken Conway's strong support.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5025272/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Chapter 47", episode_number: "S4, Ep8", description: "\nFormidable as ever, Frank and Claire have their eyes on the big picture as they manipulate a potential running mate and push a gun bill.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5095720/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Chapter 48", episode_number: "S4, Ep9", description: "\nAt the convention, Frank and his team publicly push for Secretary of State Durant to be chosen as his running mate, but privately push a different agenda.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5083704/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Chapter 49", episode_number: "S4, Ep10", description: "\nAs Frank deals with a new threat to his candidacy, Claire has doubts about their plan. Claire faces a difficult decision concerning her mother's health.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5095730/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Chapter 50", episode_number: "S4, Ep11", description: "\nFrank ups the ante on the war on terror to counter Conway's public criticism of his lack of action. Tom joins Claire on the campaign trail.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5095732/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Chapter 51", episode_number: "S4, Ep12", description: "\nFrank asks Conway to help deal with extremists threatening to murder hostages. Tom Hammerschmidt digs deeper into the allegations against Frank.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5095742/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Chapter 52", episode_number: "S4, Ep13", description: "\nAs the hostage situation continues, Claire secretly negotiates with an extremist leader. Frank confronts Hammerschmidt.    ", season_id: 2470, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5095748/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Chapter 27", episode_number: "S3, Ep1", description: "\nFrank's approval ratings have plummeted. Doug goes through rehab over his injury. Claire plans to run for Ambassador to the U.N.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3513862/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Chapter 28", episode_number: "S3, Ep2", description: "\nClaire's U.N. bid runs into trouble. Frank fights off mutiny with a bold address to the country.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3892086/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Chapter 29", episode_number: "S3, Ep3", description: "\nThe Russian president's state visit becomes a cold war of wills.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3892088/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Chapter 30", episode_number: "S3, Ep4", description: "\nClaire bypasses Russia at the U.N. Frank tries to outmaneuver a potential challenger and ends up face to face with a higher power.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3892094/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Chapter 31", episode_number: "S3, Ep5", description: "\nFrank declares war on Congress to jump-start his jobs program. Claire spars with the Russian Ambassador.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3897442/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Chapter 32", episode_number: "S3, Ep6", description: "\nFrank and Claire travel to Moscow to negotiate the return of an imprisoned U.S. citizen. Claire takes a stand that jeopardizes their plans.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3897454/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Chapter 33", episode_number: "S3, Ep7", description: "\nThe damage is done and the Underwoods must repair it. But deep wounds don't heal fast, and sometimes not at all.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3918768/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Chapter 34", episode_number: "S3, Ep8", description: "\nA hurricane endangers more than just the entire East Coast and Frank must make a difficult choice.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4083028/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Chapter 35", episode_number: "S3, Ep9", description: "\nThe Jordan Valley erupts in chaos just as Frank's campaign is picking up steam. Claire gets disturbing intel and counsels him.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4035250/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Chapter 36", episode_number: "S3, Ep10", description: "\nFrank needs to deal with Petrov one on one, while Claire tries to preserve the peace-keeping mission. Sacrifices must be made.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4128566/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Chapter 37", episode_number: "S3, Ep11", description: "\nThings turn ugly when Frank, Jackie, and Heather square off during their first debate. Tom joins Claire on the campaign trail.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4128572/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Chapter 38", episode_number: "S3, Ep12", description: "\nClaire is given an even larger role in the campaign. The gain in points drives Heather to look for dirt on Claire.    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4128574/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Chapter 39", episode_number: "S3, Ep13", description: "\nFrancis and Claire's relationship reaches a critical point. Doug catches up with his past    ", season_id: 2471, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4221826/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Chapter 14", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nFrank prepares for his promotion to Vice President. Doug tries to erase all leads leading back to him and Frank. Claire fights back against Gillian. Zoe considers working with Frank again.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2811510/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Chapter 15", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nFrank is announced as Vice President. The US meets with China. Jackie faces obstacles as she plans to run for new whip. Lucas looks into Zoe's death.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3221190/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Chapter 16", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nThe tension between Francis and Raymond Tusk increases while the situation in China is getting worse. A fight in the Senate puts Francis against the republicans.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2990016/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Chapter 17", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nA Terror threat traps Francis in the Congress building with a bitter Donald Blythe. Claire gives a live interview that shakes the media.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3001906/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Chapter 18", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nFrancis resorts to informal negotiations with a Chinese billionaire. Lucas takes extreme measures in use to reveal the vice president. Team Underwood gets a new member.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3001926/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Chapter 19", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nIn the middle of an energy crisis, Francis and Tusk end their fragile alliance. Lucas must make a difficult choice. Stamper gets closer to Rachel.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3221232/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Chapter 20", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nDespite friction, the friendship between the Walkers and the Underwoods becomes stronger. But there's a war between Francis and Tusk.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3147682/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Chapter 21", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nThe war with Tusk intensified. Claire influences Tricia Walker, both on the political and domestic front.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3147690/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Chapter 22", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nIt becomes personal when Tusk hits the Underwood pair with a scandal. Freddy and his restaurant will be involved in it all.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3186026/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Chapter 23", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nWith a military stalemate abroad and a possible violent situation at home, Francis wants to put an end to Tusk forever. Claire and Jackie Sharp collide.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3221270/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Chapter 24", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nFrank is questioned by a special prosecutor. Remy Danton is trying to keep all options open. Stamper is struggling with his demons.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3297502/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Chapter 25", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nFrancis feels shut out. Stamper tries to regain control.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3326204/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Chapter 26", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nFrancis is about to be destroyed while the nation is in turmoil. Stamper must pick up loose ends. Claire marks the conclusion of her ruthlessness.    ", season_id: 2472, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3326208/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Chapter 1", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nCongressman Francis Underwood has been declined the chair for Secretary of State. He's now gathering his own team to plot his revenge. Zoe Barnes, a reporter for the Washington Herald, will do anything to get her big break.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2161930/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Chapter 2", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nFrancis and Doug plan to frame Secretary of State nominee, Michael Kern. Meanwhile, Zoe's popularity at the Washington Herald continues to grow.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2250466/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Chapter 3", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nFrancis heads for his hometown to deal with a crisis. Zoe negotiates the politics of being a journalist on the rise. Claire finds herself a new business partner.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2248444/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Chapter 4", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nFrancis shakes down the Congressional leadership. Zoe is offered the promotion of White House Correspondent and doesn't know if she should take it or not.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2248422/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Chapter 5", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nA feud starts between Francis and Marty Spinella. Russo goes into depression about the job losses at the shipyards.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2294870/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Chapter 6", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nThe strike between Frank and Marty starts to get out of hand. Russo has decided to run for Governor of Pennsylvania.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2311910/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Chapter 7", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nFrank helps Peter get ready for his governor race, but Peter is starting to have second thoughts. Doug tries to help a young hooker in trouble.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2311926/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Chapter 8", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nFrank has a library named after him at his old military school. Peter tries to win back the support of his hometown.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2312714/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Chapter 9", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nFrank tries to do whatever it takes to get the new bill past congress. Russo goes on a bus campaign with the Vice President, but the VP is not making it an easy trip for him. Zoe's relationship with Frank gets a little bumpy.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2248426/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Chapter 10", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nTold that Claire was behind the watershed bill's failure, Francis works to contain the damage and maintain control over Peter Russo. Zoe and Claire each seek relief from their respective relationships with Francis.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2468204/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Chapter 11", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nFollowing the collapse of Russo's campaign, Francis launches a risky ploy to join the Walker administration.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2440660/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Chapter 12", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nThe President sends Frank to St. Louis to persuade Raymond Tusk into becoming the new Vice President. Zoe and Janine investigate Peter Russo's death.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2555986/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Chapter 13", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nFrank scrambles to keep his plan on track. Gillian is planning to sue Claire. Zoe, Janine, and Lucas investigate Rachel Posner and her relationship with Peter Russo.    ", season_id: 2473, series_id: 25, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2555988/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
