  {title: "Episode #6.1", episode_number: "S6, Ep1", description: "\nSPOILER: After signing a plea deal to spare his colleagues at Pearson Specter Litt Mike will be confronted with the harsh realities of prison life as he starts his two year sentence. Meanwhile the once bustling Pearson Specter Litt offices are a ghost town the partners have defected leaving Harvey Jessica, Louis, Donna and Rachel to pick up the pieces. But the firms troubles are far from over, and they will have to deal with the fallout from Mikes crime before they can even begin to rebuild.    ", season_id: 2505, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-07-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5498940/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Episode #6.2", episode_number: "S6, Ep2", description: "\n  Know what this is about?\n Be the first one to add a plot.\n    ", season_id: 2505, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-09-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5513372/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Denial", episode_number: "S5, Ep1", description: "\nMike and Rachel's engagement is put on the back burner as Donna leaves Harvey to work for Louis. Harvey is in denial and is confident she will return, but will he be able to handle it when he discovers she's not bluffing?    ", season_id: 2506, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-06-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4503862/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Compensation", episode_number: "S5, Ep2", description: "\nJessica thinks that Harvey is putting out his \"Donna anger\" on Louis, as an ambitious senior partner tries to take on Harvey's salary. Rachel's dad insists that Mike and Rachel sign a prenup.    ", season_id: 2506, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-07-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4649068/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
