  {title: "Derailed", episode_number: "S4, Ep14", description: "\nMike takes on a whistleblower case at professor Gerard's request, and Jeff uses the office receptionists to get under Louis' skin.    ", season_id: 2507, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3951374/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Intent", episode_number: "S4, Ep15", description: "\nHarvey finds out that Donna may have broken the law to help Mike get a document in the whistleblower case, but he may not be able to save her. Meanwhile, Jessica tries to figure out her next step in her relationship with Jeff.    ", season_id: 2507, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4434386/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Not Just a Pretty Face", episode_number: "S4, Ep16", description: "\nSean Cahill comes to Harvey asking for one more chance to take a shot at Charles Forstman, and Donna is left with a tough decision after Louis' secretary Norma dies.    ", season_id: 2507, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4454772/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "The Arrangement", episode_number: "S3, Ep1", description: "\nJessica's new partnership with Darby is tested when he assigns Harvey a high-profile client who faces the loss of her company if Harvey can't prove her innocence.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-07-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2529130/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "I Want You to Want Me", episode_number: "S3, Ep2", description: "\nLouis offers Mike a case that could change his future at the firm. Also, Harvey and Jessica team up to bring down an old nemesis who complicates their case to keep Ava Hessington out of jail.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-07-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2850832/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Unfinished Business", episode_number: "S3, Ep3", description: "\nCameron Dennis strikes back at Harvey by arresting one of his clients for murder. Meanwhile, Katrina Bennet and a British version of Harvey arrive to stir things up at the firm.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-07-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2983982/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Conflict of Interest", episode_number: "S3, Ep4", description: "\nHarvey's defense of Ava hits a roadblock when the interests of her murder trial are at odds with Louis' work to thwart a hostile takeover of Hessington Oil by a rival businessman.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-08-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2983986/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Shadow of a Doubt", episode_number: "S3, Ep5", description: "\nHarvey and Mike try to find a way to get Cameron removed as the prosecutor of Ava's case. When Stephen learns of their plan he offers to help and even bets Harvey that his idea will work. So Harvey kicks Mike off the case. so Mike works on a different case and asks Rachel to work with him. It involves proving a man embezzled from their client and getting him to return the money. They talk to some of the people he works with and discover that one of the women he works with, is involved with him. And they try to get her to testify against him. And Mike joins Rachel when...    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-08-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2983988/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The Other Time", episode_number: "S3, Ep6", description: "\nCameron's continuing use of shady tactics on Ava's case brings up memories of why Harvey left the DA's office to work for Jessica. Mike looks back on what cost him his one chance at a degree.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-08-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2983994/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "She's Mine", episode_number: "S3, Ep7", description: "\nHarvey clashes with Stephen over Ava's case. Also, Louis enlists Rachel in his battle with Nigel over a broken contract...and heart.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-08-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2983996/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Endgame", episode_number: "S3, Ep8", description: "\nAs Ava Hessington's murder trial begins. Harvey, Mike and Jessica fight off betrayal from both inside the firm and out. Meanwhile, Louis and Donna seek to even the score with those who have done them wrong.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-09-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3053154/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Bad Faith", episode_number: "S3, Ep9", description: "\nPearson Darby Specter's \"divorce\" brings trust issues to the forefront. Also, Mike asks Rachel to take a big step forward in their relationship.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-09-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3132574/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Stay", episode_number: "S3, Ep10", description: "\nAva Hessington hires Travis Tanner to handle her malpractice suit against the firm. And he rekindles his rivalry with Harvey. And he deposes him and even Dana. Mike finds himself in a quandary with Rachel. And when Jessica finds out about them she wants something from Rachel and tells Mike to ask her for it.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-09-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3132584/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Buried Secrets", episode_number: "S3, Ep11", description: "\nThings get complicated when Harvey (Gabriel Macht) mixes business with pleasure and gets caught between Jessica (Gina Torres) and Scottie (guest star Abigail Spencer). Painful memories plague Mike (Patrick J. Adams) as he uses a case to exorcise demons against an old foe, while Louis' (Rick Hoffman) suspicions threaten to expose Mike.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3563802/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Yesterday's Gone", episode_number: "S3, Ep12", description: "\nLouis is prepared to use the smoking gun that proves once and for all that Mike did not attend Harvard, and Jessica clashes with her ex-husband's widow and lawyer when he dies and she is named executor of his will.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3570124/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Moot Point", episode_number: "S3, Ep13", description: "\nHarvey finally gets his chance to take on Elliott Stemple, a man who beat Harvey three times in moot court and has avoided him since. Meanwhile, Dana Scott picks a fight with Louis.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3591456/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Heartburn", episode_number: "S3, Ep14", description: "\nWhile Harvey and Mike have unpleasant work to do for one of their biggest clients, Louis faces a huge challenge and Rachel tries to collect on an old debt.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3599424/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Know When to Fold 'Em", episode_number: "S3, Ep15", description: "\nA persistent attorney goes after one of Harvey's clients; Mike is faced with a difficult decision; former name partner Charles Van Dyke returns with revenge on his mind.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3607734/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "No Way Out", episode_number: "S3, Ep16", description: "\nMike is brought into the US Attorneys office for questioning by an Attorney who hates dirty lawyers. Meanwhile, Dana Scott re-evaluates her relationship with Harvey.    ", season_id: 2508, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3639420/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "She Knows", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nWhen Jessica learns about Mike, she tells Harvey, thinking that he doesn't know, and tells him to fire him. But Harvey tries to stall hoping to find a way not to. And when Daniel Hardman, the Hardman in Pearson Hardman, decides to return to the firm, Jessica is not happy about that.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-06-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2185442/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The Choice", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nWith Hardman back and knowing that it's a matter of time before he challenges Jessica for control. She decides to make sure she has enough support. So she asks Harvey to go out and get it. Problem is that he rubbed so many members of the firm the wrong way. He tries to get the head of the firm's bankruptcy department to side with Jessica when the time comes but the man feels Jessica treats him like dirt. Harvey tries to get his support by trying to get a man who is building a building that's over budget, to declare bankruptcy. But the man doesn't want to do it so ...    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-06-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2397283/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Meet the New Boss", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nWhen Hardman comes in, he tries to ingratiate himself by asking Jessica to let him handle a case wherein they're trying to keep some nurses from going on strike by negotiating a contract. But Jessica says that she already gave it to Harvey which was a lie. And Hardman tries to horn in by getting Mike to give him some info. And Jessica tells Louis that Harvard is considering not allowing them to recruit because the firm's approval rating is low. So he brings in someone from Harvard to check them out but she tells Louis something that he doesn't like.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-06-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2199752/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Discovery", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nAlicia and Lucca help Louis defend ChumHum against accusations of racial profiling in its mapping systems, and Eli tries to figure out the full nature of Alicia and Jason's relationship.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2199756/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Break Point", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nHarvey balks when Jessica puts him in the passenger seat on a lawsuit that could make or break the firm, and his back seat driving may have far reaching consequences. Mike takes the lead on a case that pits a tennis phenom against his trainer who also happens to be the athlete's father.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-07-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2253942/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "All In", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nHarvey's personal history with a client forces he and Mike to take on an unorthodox case from which they'd normally walk away. Louis and Rachel team up to save a mutually beloved institution from ruin. Jessica runs into an unexpected roadblock while defending the firm against a lawsuit.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-07-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2199758/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Sucker Punch", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nWhile investigating the death of an Irish mobster, Beckett and Castle uncover a local turf war that may be connected to both a late-night infomercial guru and an international drug smuggling operation. But the case turns agonizingly personal when evidence emerges that the killer they're chasing may have had a hand in Beckett's mother's murder.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-01-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2268628/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Rewind", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nWith the vote for managing partner approaching, Harvey decides to take off but before leaving he gives Mike an assignment. We then take a look at of how things were 5 years ago; Harvey is an associate and Hardman was still managing partner and Jessica learns that someone in the firm is stealing so she has Harvey find out who. Mike is struggling to make ends meet after getting kicked out of school and how he and Trevor first met Jenny and how her friend takes a special interest in Mike.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-08-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2305044/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Asterisk", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nHarvey and Jessica get ready for the vote. They learn that the vote is split after Hardman got rid of one of Jessica's supporters and that Hardman made Louis a Senior Partner and as a result is the deciding vote. Jessica wants Harvey to get him to vote for her. Harvey and Mike are working on a case wherein a reporter is being sued by a baseball player when he accuses the man of using steroids. The reporter claims the story is accurate because he has a source whom he will not reveal. And Mike's grandmother comes to the office.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-08-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2310538/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "High Noon", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nFinally, the voting occurs and, seems Hardman wins by the vote of Louis. Hardman and Louis make Harvey's life hell and Mike goes wayward with death of his granny. Having a night-out with Mike, Harvey catches Louis in his office and the whole conspiracy game by Hardman comes out. Mike throws a trick and Hardman gets voted out of the firm. The unfolding of the conspiracy makes a really interesting climax...    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-08-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2310526/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Blind-Sided", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nMike gets too emotional when Harvey asks him to negotiate a hit-and-run settlement, and Louis runs into trouble as he tries to hire his first associate.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2583678/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Blood in the Water", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nAnother firm, led by a familiar face, makes an aggressive play to steal Pearson Hardman's associates and clients, and the fallout could affect Louis Litt's future at the firm.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2583680/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Zane vs. Zane", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nRachel's father becomes the defense attorney in a gender discrimination lawsuit being prosecuted by Pearson Hardman, and Louis wages war against the new associate hired by Harvey.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2583682/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "He's Back", episode_number: "S2, Ep14", description: "\nDaniel Hardman plays a dirty trick his old firm when he takes over the defense in the gender discrimination case, and Rachel has second thoughts about applying to Harvard Law School.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2660120/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Normandy", episode_number: "S2, Ep15", description: "\nHarvey joins forces with and old familiar face to take down Daniel Hardman, Mike and Katrina play a sneaky game of one-upsmanship, and Rachel gets some bad news about her Harvard application.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2671864/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "War", episode_number: "S2, Ep16", description: "\nHarvey puts his name partnership on the line to prevent the merger from going through, Louis clashes his counterpart from the other firm, and Rachel puts Mike in a no-win situation by asking for a recommendation to Harvard.    ", season_id: 2509, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2560618/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Pilot", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nA \"closer\" for one of New York City's most successful law firms decides to hire an aloof genius who has passed the bar but never went to law school as his associate.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-06-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1973786/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Errors and Omissions", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nHarvey discovers that the judge in his patent case has a personal vendetta against him, while Louis tries to blackmail Mike in order to get his help bringing in a valuable client.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-06-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1973785/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Inside Track", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nHarvey asks Mike to find a loophole so that he can oust the incoming CEO of a motor company he represents, while Louis puts outrageous demands on Mike as he tries to make arrangements for the Rookie Dinner.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-07-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1976882/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Dirty Little Secrets", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nHarvey defends someone from Jessica's past. Meanwhile, Mike is assigned his first solo case and his secret is almost discovered.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-07-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1977541/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Bail Out", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nHarvey is a witness for his driver in a civil suit, and has to rely on Louis for help. Mike bails his old friend Trevor out of jail.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-07-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2003931/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Tricks of the Trade", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nHarvey and Mike try to prove that a woman accused of insider trading is innocent. Mike also tries to help Rachel study for the LSAT, but he soon finds out she is close to uncovering his secret.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-07-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1973787/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Play the Man", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nMike takes on Louis' protégé during a mock trial, but his conflict with Rachel could hurt his chances of winning. Elsewhere, Harvey works on a merger between two hotel chains, but his past with the opposing counsel complicates matters.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-08-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1987364/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Identity Crisis", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nHarvey and Louis come to blows after Louis' reckless behavior threatens to cost the firm a case, while Mike is assigned to a businessman who is trying to get back money from his estranged daughter.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-08-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1987365/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Undefeated", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nHarvey meets his match in a cocky opposing counsel in a class action lawsuit, and Mike unknowingly helps frame Rachel as a traitor to the firm.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-08-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1985804/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The Shelf Life", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nHarvey must fire an accountant for falsifying his credentials, but Mike finds a more sinister motive for his termination and becomes concerned about his own employment. Meanwhile, Louis thinks he's found his future wife.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-08-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1986650/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Rules of the Game", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nHarvey is threatened with disbarment if he doesn't testify against his old mentor in the DA's office. Meanwhile, Harvey wagers Mike's services in a bet with Louis, and Mike goes out on an awkward double date.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-09-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1995990/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Dog Fight", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nIn the first-season finale, Harvey tries to free an innocent man,Clifford Danner (Neil Brown Jr.), but hits a wall when he goes to the district attorney (Chi McBride), who seems more focused on preserving the system than seeking justice. Elsewhere, Trevor causes problems for Mike when he shows up on his doorstep.    ", season_id: 2510, series_id: 31, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-09-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2014019/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
