  {title: "An Old Friend Calls", episode_number: "S3, Ep15", description: "\nWhen Klaus learns the Cortez arrival to vendetta against him, Klaus finds himself dealing with the new threat. Meanwhile, Cortez begins threatening the lives of innocent residents, Vincent has no option but to assist Vengeful Vampire in his plan to take down Klaus.    ", season_id: 2552, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4913010/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Alone with Everybody", episode_number: "S3, Ep16", description: "\nWhen rumors begin to spread about the remaining white oak bullet, dangerous foes descend upon New Orleans in an attempt to take down Klaus once and for all. As the threats continue to grow, Elijah urges his siblings to lay low at the compound while Marcel, Vincent and Josh chase down a lead involving a mysterious vampire named Sofya , who may have the answers they're looking for. Meanwhile, tensions inside the compound build as Kol is forced to come face to face with his brother Finn, the person responsible for his death. Elsewhere, Klaus and Hayley seek shelter with ...    ", season_id: 2552, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4913008/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Behind the Black Horizon", episode_number: "S3, Ep17", description: "\nWhen its discovered that Freya has been kidnapped and is in the hands of a dangerous new threat, the Mikaelson brothers are forced to put aside their differences in order to save her before it's too late. Following a lead that brings them to Mystic Falls, Elijah and Finn run into deputy Matt Donovan, who does not take well to new vampires in his town. Meanwhile, Klaus and Hayley work together to uncover the motive behind one of Lucien's secret agendas, while a troubling shift in Kol's behavior leaves Davina concerned for their future together.    ", season_id: 2552, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4913018/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "The Devil Comes Here and Sighs", episode_number: "S3, Ep18", description: "\nAs the city celebrates its annual Jazz Fest, an unlikely team of Mikaelson foes joins forces to take Klaus hostage. Leading the charge to get their brother back, Elijah and Freya face off against a powerful force like none they've ever seen before, while Hayley and Cami set their own risky plan in motion to rescue Klaus. Meanwhile, when Kol's erratic behavior worsens, Davina has no choice but to turn to Marcel and Vincent for help.    ", season_id: 2552, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4913042/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "No More Heartbreaks", episode_number: "S3, Ep19", description: "\nFollowing a violent encounter that has left Cami's life hanging in the balance, Klaus is forced to rely on his family and allies to find a cure as he keeps a watchful eye over Cami at the compound. With time running out, Freya turns to her arsenal of spells, while Vincent and Marcel head to Cami's apartment to gather a crucial ingredient. Elsewhere, Hayley and Elijah travel to the bayou in hopes of bringing back a potential antidote that could save Cami's life. Finally, Davina confronts Lucien and learns some heartbreaking information that will change her future with ...    ", season_id: 2552, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4913040/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Where Nothing Stays Buried", episode_number: "S3, Ep20", description: "\nIn the wake of a ruthless plan that has left their family shattered, Klaus, Elijah and Freya desperately search for a way to take down Lucien once and for all. However, their efforts are put on hold following an urgent plea for help from Kol and Marcel. At Klaus' insistence, Freya and Elijah reluctantly stay behind to offer their help, while Klaus and Hayley head to the bayou after uncovering Lucien's latest plan. Once there, an unexpected showdown between Klaus and Lucien forces Freya to take matters into her own hands, setting off a chain of events that will change ...    ", season_id: 2552, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4913038/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Give 'Em Hell Kid", episode_number: "S3, Ep21", description: "\nAfter receiving new visions of the looming prophecy, Freya uncovers that her family is on a collision course with a dangerous new enemy. Meanwhile, with the help of Detective Kinney, Vincent and Kol travel to the ancestral world to put a stop to the witches and take back their city once and for all. Elsewhere, Klaus and Elijah confront Marcel after a heartbreaking plan gone wrong has sent him spiraling. Hayley and Davina also appear.    ", season_id: 2552, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4913032/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "The Bloody Crown", episode_number: "S3, Ep22", description: "\nAfter months of thwarting off dangerous threats and deadly attacks, the Mikaelson siblings finally come face to face with the one person that could lead to their ultimate demise. With the stakes higher than ever and the compound overrun by an army of his oldest sworn enemies, Klaus is put on trial for centuries of atrocities he's committed. Meanwhile, Marcel, who has been spiraling out of control following an act of betrayal by those closest to him, is stunned by the unexpected arrival of someone from his past. Finally, Elijah, Freya and Kol frantically search for a ...    ", season_id: 2552, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4913030/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Rebirth", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nHayley struggles with her powers. Marcel sides with Klaus and gets revenge over the wolves. Esther is busy plotting her own plans. Everyone wants control over the city.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3532624/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Alive and Kicking", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nNathaniel appears as Kol in flashback whereas tensions between Elijah and Hayley grow, Klaus steps in and encourages her to regain her position within her werewolf pack. Mikael grows impatient under Davina's control while she attempts to uncover a spell that would protect those closest to her. Eljiah and Marcel work together to gather a vital piece of information. KLaus gets suspicious about Cassie.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3754904/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Every Mother's Son", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nWhen Klaus and Elijah receive a cryptic invitation to dinner from their mother Esther, they find themselves preparing for the worst. Esther reveals a shocking secret about Klaus' childhood and unveils her ultimate plan for her children.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787860/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Live and Let Die", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nDavina takes Mikael to a cabin to heal from his wolf bites. Klaus searches for them. Elijah, Marcel and Hayley try to rescue some young wolves.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787864/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Red Door", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nIn order to show Elijah that her plan is what's best for him, Esther forces him to relive a time long ago when he loved a young woman named Tatia.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787866/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Wheel Inside the Wheel", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nCami teams up with Marcel and Gia after she becomes suspicious of her faculty advisor Vincent. Lastly, in a surprising turn of events, Klaus comes face-to-face with a visitor from his past.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787868/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Chasing the Devil's Tail", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nGoing after everything Esther loves. Klaus and Hayley seek an antidote for Elijah in the bayou assisted by Marcel and Josh. Kaleb takes Davina to an old hangout.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787870/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "The Brothers That Care Forgot", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nRebekah is on the run with baby Hope.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787872/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The Map of Moments", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nRebekah persuades Klaus and Elijah to take part in a family tradition from their childhood.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-12-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787874/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Gonna Set Your Flag on Fire", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nFinn puts a spell on the compound, trapping wolves and vampires. Klaus takes Cami to the safe house, then confronts Kol about Rebekah's whereabouts.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787878/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Brotherhood of the Damned", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nFinn captures his brother's spirits, while the vampires remain trapped and their hunger grows.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787876/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Sanctuary", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nRebekah becomes interested in a girl. Hayley struggles with coming clean and is surprised by something Jackson admits. Klaus learns something and heads to confront Hayley. Vincent sets his eyes on Marcel for answers to what Klaus is hiding.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787886/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "The Devil Is Damned", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nVincent joins forces with a figure from his past. Kaleb is forced to make a difficult life or death decision, and Elijah finds himself in the fight of his life. Hayley and Jackson become pawns in Vincent's dangerous plan.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3787882/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "I Love You, Goodbye", episode_number: "S2, Ep14", description: "\nWith the final preparations for her union to Jackson underway, Hayley begins to question whether the ritual will actually work. After arriving to the compound, Elijah has a tense encounter with Klaus and quickly suspects that his brother may be up to something. Meanwhile, Kaleb, who is harboring a devastating secret from Davina, seeks help from Rebekah when he realizes time is not on his side. Lastly, Cami makes a startling revelation involving baby Hope.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006442/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "They All Asked for You", episode_number: "S2, Ep15", description: "\nWhen a dangerous run-in with a coven of vengeful witches forces Rebekah to align with Marcel, they quickly discover that the body Rebekah is currently inhabiting has a checkered past. Upon learning that Rebekah is in danger, Elijah seeks out a respected elder witch, Josephine, in the hopes she might offer her assistance. Meanwhile, tensions build when Klaus clashes with Hayley and Jackson over how best to protect baby Hope from Finn, Elsewhere, Freya, convinces Finn to bring her to Mikael, the father she hasn't seen in over a thousand years. Lastly, a confrontation ...    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006462/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Save My Soul", episode_number: "S2, Ep16", description: "\nSuspicious of where her true loyalties lie, Klaus invites Freya to the compound in order to gain more insight into her past with Dahlia. After a series of strange visions,Rebekah begins to realize the body she's inhabiting is attempting to regain control. With Rebekah's life on the line, Marcel puts his bargaining skills to the test when he turns to Finn, who may have some knowledge that could help them. Lastly, at the bayou, Jackson's frustrations grow after Aiden questions his leadership skills. Elijah, Hayley and Cami also appear.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006458/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Exquisite Corpse", episode_number: "S2, Ep17", description: "\nKlaus must put aside his mistrust for Freya in order to save Rebekah's life.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006464/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Night Has a Thousand Eyes", episode_number: "S2, Ep18", description: "\nWhile searching for a way to vanquish Dahlia, Klaus is faced with another threat.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006456/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "When the Levee Breaks", episode_number: "S2, Ep19", description: "\nSetting the stage for a bloody showdown, Dahlia gives Klaus and Hayley a deadline to turn over baby Hope. Elijah attempts to convince Klaus that they need to work together in their fight against Dahlia, but Klaus forges ahead with his own dangerous plan, leaving everyone concerned about his next steps. Meanwhile, when Hayley realizes their chances of outrunning Dahlia are slim, she devises a risky plan and enlists Aiden's help. Elsewhere, Freya gives Rebekah and Elijah an ultimatum, and Marcel strategizes on how best to deal with Klaus' erratic behavior.    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006454/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "City Beneath the Sea", episode_number: "S2, Ep20", description: "\nWhen Dahlia devises a clever way to get Klaus' attention, she reveals some startling details about baby Hope and leaves him with an enticing proposition to consider. Elsewhere, while Elijah and Freya find themselves with opposing views on how best to handle Dahlia's looming deadline, Rebekah, Davina and Cami work together to come up with their own strategy. Meanwhile, following a tense standoff between Elijah and Jackson in the bayou, Hayley is left to make a difficult decision about her and Hope's future. Finally, Vincent, who is eager to leave his witch past behind ...    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006472/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Fire with Fire", episode_number: "S2, Ep21", description: "\nAfter discovering that he's been betrayed by his own siblings, Klaus teams up with an unlikely ally and sets off on a warpath, hell bent on revenge. Amidst the news that Klaus is on the loose, Elijah, Rebekah and Freya move forward with their plan to lure Dahlia to the compound and take her down once and for all. Meanwhile, Hayley and Jackson attempt to escape through the flooded bayou, even as Marcel finds himself hunted by a dangerous new threat. Finally, Davina is presented with an offer that could allow her the chance to bring back Kol, though it will require her ...    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-05-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006460/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "Ashes to Ashes", episode_number: "S2, Ep22", description: "\nWith time running out, Klaus' ultimate plan to protect baby Hope at all costs continues to take shape. As tensions between the siblings come to a head, Camille reveals a vital piece of information that causes Elijah and Rebekah to reconsider their plan of attack against Dahlia. Davina finds herself one step closer to fulfilling the promise she made to Kol, while Freya is forced to take drastic measures to protect herself against Dahlia. Elsewhere, Marcel has to put aside his fury at Klaus in order to protect himself and everyone in their sire line. Meanwhile, Vincent ...    ", season_id: 2553, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-05-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4006470/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Always and Forever", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nKlaus Mikaelson, the Original vampire/werewolf hybrid, returns to the magical melting pot that is the French Quarter of New Orleans - a town he helped build centuries ago.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2879460/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "House of the Rising Son", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nRebekah arrives in New Orleans at her brother Elijah's insistence, but, concerned that Klaus is up to no good, she seeks help from a reluctant Sophie. Marcel enlists Davina's help.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065730/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Tangled Up in Blue", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nBetrayal at the masquerade ball? Klaus and Rebekah come together to attempt to unravel Marcel's empire from within, in spite of Elijah's concerns. They enlist help from Sophie.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065788/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Girl in New Orleans", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nDetermined Rebekah is on a mission to get to the bottom of a recent strange encounter involving Elijah. Davina convinces Marcel to let her attend an annual street music festival.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065790/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Sinners and Saints", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nAngered by recent events involving the safety of his unborn baby, Klaus demands answers from Sophie, believing she was involved. Sophie reveals to Klaus and Rebekah a troubling secret from her past. Meanwhile, Marcel asks Klaus to accompany him to the bayou after gruesome remains are discovered, while Rebekah, Sophie and Hayley set off on a mission of their own. Davina confides in an unexpected ally and reveals shocking information about the witches - ultimately leading to a disturbing revelation.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065104/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Fruit of the Poisoned Tree", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nWhen Klaus discovers Hayley's life is being threatened, he goes to extreme lengths to protect her and their unborn baby. Cami turns to Father Kieran for guidance when she is having a difficult time dealing with the tragic events of her past. Feeling as though he can trust no one, Marcel visits an old friend to seek out some advice, while Davina takes steps to learn how to control her magic. Finally, Klaus delivers some surprising news to Father Kieran.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065236/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Bloodletting", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nWhen someone from Hayley's past makes a startling revelation, she grows concerned for herself and the baby. Amidst growing tensions between them, Klaus and Elijah turn to Sabine for help in locating Hayley, who has gone missing. After making a trip down to the bayou, Klaus has a surprising and dangerous encounter with an unexpected visitor. Meanwhile, Davina makes a surprising connection, and Marcel makes Rebekah an enticing offer that leaves her torn.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065194/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "The River in Reverse", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nIn the war between Klaus and Marcel, Rebecca stands against her own brother Klaus. The chemistry between Elijah and Hayley gets stronger. Klaus accuses his siblings of distrust and betrayal.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065198/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Reigning Pain in New Orleans", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nKlaus tries to get adapted to his new duties as he became the king of the city. He offers Marcel a compromise and he fixes his relationship with his siblings. Davina feels betrayed by Marcel. She finally finds an allay, Cami.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-12-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065240/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The Casket Girls", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nAs the French Quarter prepares for its annual celebration of the Casket Girls Festival, Cami suffers through as Davina attempts to free her of Klaus' mind compulsion. Elijah and Marcel form an unlikely alliance as Klaus sets his plan in motion to get Davina back. Once it's known that Davina is missing, Sophie gets in on the hunt to track her down. Meanwhile, Hayley is forced to make a tough decision after receiving an unexpected phone call, and Rebekah sets her own plan in motion when she enlists the help of someone from Marcel's past.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065234/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Après Moi, Le Déluge", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nWhen Davina becomes violently ill and the repercussions soon begin to affect the entire French Quarter, Marcel, Klaus, Elijah and Rebekah rush to find out what is going on. Sophie approaches the others with some startling information about the Harvest Festival and presents a drastic plan to save Davina. Elsewhere, Hayley is racked with guilt as she comes clean to Elijah about her role in Sophie's plan. Last, a sequence of unforeseen events sends shockwaves through the French Quarter.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3065244/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Dance Back from the Grave", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nMarcel, still angered refuses to help Klaus when a gruesome discovery is made. Rebekah is on alert when she uncovers the remnants of a sacrifice down by the docks realizing it's the work of a dangerous warlock from their past. when Elijah gets some information that Rebekah may be in trouble, he and Hayley set off to find her. Camille confronts Marcel, who opens up and shares some details of his past with her, but things quickly spiral out of control when an unexpected visitor shows up. Finally, a violent confrontation ensues when Klaus faces off against a powerful ...    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3188842/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Crescent City", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nAt the re-opening of St. Anne's Church, Father Kieran finds himself in a great deal of trouble after a run-in with a witch from his past. Marcel and Rebekah grow concerned when the reemergence of someone they once knew threatens to expose secrets they've kept buried for nearly a century. Elsewhere, Sophie is shocked when a discovery is made at the cemetery, but she soon realizes things may not be as they seem. With the full moon looming, Hayley lets Rebekah in on her plan to throw a party for her werewolf clan, but things take a dangerous turn when uninvited guests ...    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3188846/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Long Way Back from Hell", episode_number: "S1, Ep14", description: "\nRebekah's past comes back to haunt her.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3259202/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Le Grand Guignol", episode_number: "S1, Ep15", description: "\nIn a series of flashbacks to 1919, Klaus opens up to Cami and reveals details of the devastating secret Rebekah and Marcel were trying to keep from him. Elijah forms an unlikely alliance with Monique and asks for her help in locating Sabine. Elsewhere, Thierry is reluctant to get involved when Marcel and Rebekah approach him with a plan to take down the witches. Meanwhile, in the bayou, Hayley is at her wits' end and holds Sabine hostage in an attempt to get information that will reverse the curse on Hayley's werewolf clan.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3259208/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Farewell to Storyville", episode_number: "S1, Ep16", description: "\nSince the original vampires were stuck in the cemetery, Klaus takes any chances to punish his sister with the Original-killer stake.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3259210/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Moon Over Bourbon Street", episode_number: "S1, Ep17", description: "\nElijah is taking control of the quarter and receives a surprising offer, and they know how to throw a party.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3329322/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "The Big Uneasy", episode_number: "S1, Ep18", description: "\n\"Genevieve asks Elijah to allow her coven to publicly celebrate a traditional feast day, where members of the community offer the witches gifts in return for blessings. Monique and Genevieve disagree over what the ancestors want from them, and Genevieve reveals her plan to build the witches' power. When Elijah focuses his attention on restoring their home to its former glory, Klaus accuses him of doing it only to impress Hayley . Next, Klaus sets a new plan in motion by finding Cary , a werewolf from his own line, and sending him off to find a missing piece of family ...    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3329324/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "An Unblinking Death", episode_number: "S1, Ep19", description: "\nDesperate to help Kieran, Camille insists on an unconventional treatment, but her good intentions lead Kieran to a violent episode. After Klaus and Elijah disagree over the best way to handle the Crescent Wolves, Elijah makes a trip to the bayou, where he is witness to a horrific explosion that only adds to the hatred and mistrust among the communities. While Jackson and Elijah work to save the wounded, Hayley learns a surprising piece of her family history from Marcel.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3329330/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "A Closer Walk with Thee", episode_number: "S1, Ep20", description: "\nHayley confronts a surprising enemy as she and her unborn baby fall into peril during a celebratory wake to honor a fallen member of the community. In order to save Hayley, Klaus and Elijah enlist the help of Genevieve who struggles to maintain control over Davina and the other young witches. Camille tells Marcel that Francesca is determined to find a mysterious key that may unlock a family secret. Meanwhile, as Klaus suffers from nightmares of his father Mikael, he is forced to examine his troubled relationship with his own adoptive son, Marcel.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3329328/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "The Battle of New Orleans", episode_number: "S1, Ep21", description: "\nKlaus and Elijah enact a plan to collect the sacred stones needed by Genevieve in order to forever change the fates of Hayley and the werewolf community. Realizing that Klaus' plan will lead to the extermination of all French Quarter vampires, Marcel rallies an army determined to take down the Mikaelsons and regain control of the city. Davina warns Josh to leave town as she is forced to make a fateful decision that will turn the tide of war. Meanwhile, Francesca threatens Cami, who attempts to decipher a code that results in a surprising revelation among the city's ...    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3329332/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "From a Cradle to a Grave", episode_number: "S1, Ep22", description: "\nAs the baby's due date draws near, Klaus and Elijah embark on a search for Hayley, while Hayley determines to do whatever it takes to keep her unborn baby safe and away from the witches. Francesca takes a meeting with Oliver and Jackson to determine the future of the werewolves in New Orleans. In the aftermath of a surprising attack on Marcel and his vampires at the compound, Davina and Cami join resources to take down Klaus. Finally, in a desperate move to protect those most important to him, Klaus makes a heartbreaking decision.    ", season_id: 2554, series_id: 40, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3329334/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Bond", episode_number: "S7, Ep1", description: "\nAs Alicia struggles to get her career back on track, she stumbles on a case that puts her up against Diane Lockhart and David Lee. Peter fires Eli Gold, who vows revenge. Cary discovers that his firm is getting out of touch.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4836976/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Innocents", episode_number: "S7, Ep2", description: "\nAlicia hires a new investigator, and a new friend from bond court helps her with a case. Eli uses Alicia to maneuver his way back into Peter's campaign. Cary looks for a way to get Howard out of the firm.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5039420/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Cooked", episode_number: "S7, Ep3", description: "\nAlicia and Lucca work together on a complicated court case involving a designer drug dealer. Also, Eli encourages Alicia and Veronica (Stockard Channing) to participate in a mother/daughter cooking show to help Peter's campaign, with disastrous results.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5056736/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Taxed", episode_number: "S7, Ep4", description: "\nAlicia clashes with the bond court judge when she agrees to support a client's plea of innocence in a shoplifting case. Diane is coerced by her client's counsel to argue against her own beliefs in a case about physician assisted suicide.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-10-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4959558/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Payback", episode_number: "S7, Ep5", description: "\nAlicia and Lucca take on a for-profit university, while Jason tries to recover a missing student loan payment. Meanwhile, Eli creates more havoc for Peter's campaign, and Diane looks for a solution after Howard accuses Cary of ageism.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4981390/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Lies", episode_number: "S7, Ep6", description: "\nAlicia needs help from an old friend to win a case involving the NSA. Eli tries to sabotage Peter's presidential candidate announcement. A minority applicant puts Lockhart Agos Lee in hot water. Alicia begins looking into Jason's past.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5126964/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Driven", episode_number: "S7, Ep7", description: "\nAlicia, Cary and Louis all oppose each other in a case involving driverless cars. Things become awkward at home when Peter is forced to stay to keep up appearances. Alicia is in an awkward position in her first Election Committee vote.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5146926/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Restraint", episode_number: "S7, Ep8", description: "\nDiane defends a client that could hurt her reputation and cost her clients, Grace tries to drum up new business for Alicia and Lucca, and Eli puts political pressure on Courtney Paige to change a business decision that could hurt Peter.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5193328/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Discovery", episode_number: "S7, Ep9", description: "\nAlicia and Lucca help Louis defend ChumHum against accusations of racial profiling in its mapping systems, and Eli tries to figure out the full nature of Alicia and Jason's relationship.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5201688/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "KSR", episode_number: "S7, Ep10", description: "\nAlicia defends a doctor who faces criminal charges for rape fantasies, A group of associates leaves Lockhart Agos Lee high and dry, Ruth plots to get rid of Jason, and Eli's feelings for Paige end in heartbreak and a surprise confession.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-12-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5225466/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Iowa", episode_number: "S7, Ep11", description: "\nPeter tries to make a strong showing in the Iowa Caucus, but Alicia is still giving the cold shoulder to Eli. Lucca makes a discovery while setting up Jackie and Howard's prenup. Diane and Cary have to answer to a discrimination accusation.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5265742/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Tracks", episode_number: "S7, Ep12", description: "\nA client is infatuated with Lucca, Alicia discovers that Lockhart Agos Lee is trying to poach their new clients, Alicia's homeowner's association tries to evict her, and Eli enlists help to win Alicia's forgiveness.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5276592/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Judged", episode_number: "S7, Ep13", description: "\nAfter an unsuccessful lawsuit against Judge Schakowsky, Jason's return to Chicago, and a looming malpractice suit, Alicia reaches her breaking point. Meanwhile Diane takes on a private college defunding and shutting down its newspaper.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5264354/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Monday", episode_number: "S7, Ep14", description: "\nAlicia has another bout with ChumHum as she and Lucca return to her old firm. However, she also discovers that Cary is trying to split Lucca and her up, and Eli discovers that she is a possible target in a federal investigation.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5368048/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Targets", episode_number: "S7, Ep15", description: "\nAlicia sits on a panel deciding whether to attack and kill an American-born ISIS recruiter. Eli hires Elsbeth Tascioni to help find out who's investigating Peter and why. David Lee hires Jason to investigate Diane's motives with the firm.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5431472/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Hearing", episode_number: "S7, Ep16", description: "\nEli is desperate to find out what the grand jury hearing involving Peter is specifically about, Alicia's mother Veronica needs help after she is scammed, and Diane comes to Alicia with a business proposition.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5462486/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Shoot", episode_number: "S7, Ep17", description: "\nDiane defends a grieving father who made a billboard blaming a gun seller for his daughter's death. Alicia and Jason's romance hits a snag. Eli has a plan to exploit his advantage in Peter's grand jury hearing.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5456198/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Unmanned", episode_number: "S7, Ep18", description: "\nAlicia and Peter go to war after he learns of her affair. The male partners challenge Diane over the future of the firm. Eli has to protect his daughter from a legal dilemma. Diane and Alicia take a case involving drones and privacy.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5525324/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Landing", episode_number: "S7, Ep19", description: "\nAlicia and Lucca travel to Toronto to represent NSA Agent Jeff Delinger who was detained by customs officers while attempting to re-enter the United States. Also, Diane grows concerned when her husband, Kurt McVeigh, decides to retire and sell his business to Holly Westfall, a rival business owner, and Peter contemplates an uncertain future when he faces possible arrest.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5502700/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Party", episode_number: "S7, Ep20", description: "\nAlicia's night goes from bad to worse when she throws a party to celebrate Howard and Jackie's upcoming wedding. Also, Eli asks Jason to investigate Peter in preparation for his trial.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5525326/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Verdict", episode_number: "S7, Ep21", description: "\nPeter looks like he's in big trouble as his trial progresses,and some old friends are placed in difficult situations. Diane faces unexpected opposition from David Lee as the new firm moves forward.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5525328/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "End", episode_number: "S7, Ep22", description: "\nPeter has little time left to make a plea deal before the jury comes back with a verdict. Meanwhile, Alicia must decide whether her future is with Peter or with Jason, and she channels the ghost of Will Gardner to help make a decision.    ", season_id: 2555, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5447674/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "The Line", episode_number: "S6, Ep1", description: "\nDiane is planning to \"retire\" from her firm to join Florrick Agos, but everything is put on hold when Cary is arrested on serious drug charges. Meanwhile, Eli plots to launch Alicia as a candidate for state's attorney.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3596120/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Trust Issues", episode_number: "S6, Ep2", description: "\nAlicia has to defend ChumHum in a lawsuit while also trying to secure bail money for Cary. Meanwhile, more lawyers may join Diane as she jumps ship to Florrick Agos, and Eli continues to pressure Alicia to run for office.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-09-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3899742/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Dear God", episode_number: "S6, Ep3", description: "\nCary is in danger of losing his bail, and one of Alicia's clients opts to take his case to Christian arbitration. Meanwhile, a feminist icon encourages Alicia to run for office, but she still refuses to take the bait.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4018700/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Oppo Research", episode_number: "S6, Ep4", description: "\nAlicia decides to run for state's attorney, but she is not prepared to hear all the dirt that her campaign manager has gathered about her own family and career.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4074858/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Shiny Objects", episode_number: "S6, Ep5", description: "\nAlicia faces a dilemma as she kicks off her campaign, the firm's computers are held for ransom by a con artist, and Alicia tries to throw Elsbeth Tascioni off her game as they go head-to-head in a trial.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4083504/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Old Spice", episode_number: "S6, Ep6", description: "\nCary violates his bail agreement on a technicality, Alicia addresses her religious beliefs for her campaign, Diane plots to evict her old firm, and Elsbeth has feelings for her opposing A.U.S.A. counsel.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4030396/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Message Discipline", episode_number: "S6, Ep7", description: "\nFinn Polmar devises a new strategy to go after Cary, which could have a negative affect on governor Florrick. Meanwhile, a potential new candidate in the state's attorney race could challenge Alicia's front-runner status.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4128270/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Red Zone", episode_number: "S6, Ep8", description: "\nAlicia gives legal advice to a rape victim and winds up dealing with a trial against Louis Canning, while also trying to improve her image for the the election. Meanwhile, Lemond Bishop is suspicious of Kalinda's lover, Lana.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4155544/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Sticky Content", episode_number: "S6, Ep9", description: "\nAfter Prady goes to Alicia with an intriguing proposal involving their campaigns, Alicia discovers that Peter may be seeing another woman. Meanwhile, Cary learns that Lemond Bishop may be trying to kill him.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4155550/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The Trial", episode_number: "S6, Ep10", description: "\nWhen Cary's case goes to trial, a plea deal offer has him seriously considering jail time. Also, a joke between mother and daughter lands Alicia in trouble as her campaign for State's Attorney is in full stride.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4197012/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Hail Mary", episode_number: "S6, Ep11", description: "\nWhile the Florrick camp tries to prepare Alicia for her debate with Prady, the firm launches a last-ditch effort to save Cary before he is scheduled to go to prison.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4277078/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "The Debate", episode_number: "S6, Ep12", description: "\nA new rumor of Peter's infidelity is leaked to Alicia moments before her debate, but social unrest over a courtroom verdict puts the debate on hold. Meanwhile, a messy divorce settlement cause Cary and Diane to make a deal with the Devil.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4244648/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Dark Money", episode_number: "S6, Ep13", description: "\nThe firm takes on a TV producer who made an episode based on the Colin Sweeney murder case, Alicia and Prady compete for a wealthy donor's campaign money, and Lemond Bishop makes Kalinda drive his son home from school.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4340768/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Mind's Eye", episode_number: "S6, Ep14", description: "\nAs Alicia prepares for an important interview, rumors of her campaign partnership with Lemond Bishop swirl. But Alicia is distracted thinking about a lawsuit from Canning, troubles with her kids, and her ongoing love for Will Gardner.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4453196/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Open Source", episode_number: "S6, Ep15", description: "\nA case involving a gun made from a 3D printer causes tension between Diane and Kurt McVeigh, Alicia must decide whether to make a political attack against her husband, and Canning has an odd request for Alicia after his transplant.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4472254/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Red Meat", episode_number: "S6, Ep16", description: "\nPeter deliberately sabotages Alicia's chances of victory the morning of the election, Diane tries to court a billionaire for the firm at a hunting retreat, and a new tail causes new problems for Kalinda and Lemond Bishop.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4419978/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Undisclosed Recipients", episode_number: "S6, Ep17", description: "\nAfter Alicia's election victory, her biggest campaign donors come to her with their demands. Meanwhile, negotiations for Alicia's severance package is put on hold by an unexpected, potentially devastating hack of the firm's emails.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4523502/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Loser Edit", episode_number: "S6, Ep18", description: "\nWhen Eli finds out a reporter has a copy of Alicia's incriminating emails, he tries to get ahead of the story. Meanwhile, Kalinda finds herself in potentially huge trouble, and Diane debates gay marriage with a conservative think tank.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4529816/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Winning Ugly", episode_number: "S6, Ep19", description: "\nWhile facing accusations of election fraud, Alicia learns about the dark side of politics the hard way. Meanwhile, Kalinda's actions related to Cary's case threaten to get Diane disbarred, but there could be a way out.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4559186/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "The Deconstruction", episode_number: "S6, Ep20", description: "\nAlicia's return to the firm after she withdraws from the election is sidetracked by mistrust on both sides. Meanwhile, Kalinda has a plan to turn on Bishop and not get caught, and Diane considers a test case to challenge mandatory minimums.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4562978/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Don't Fail", episode_number: "S6, Ep21", description: "\nWith her election troubles and problems at her old firm, Alicia's self-confidence is at an all-time low. However, an opportunity to revisit a case from her past when new charges are presented rekindles her love for the law.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-05-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4614806/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "Wanna Partner?", episode_number: "S6, Ep22", description: "\nPeter eyes a run for president with Alicia's approval, Finn and Alicia help a client who may be illegally detained, Bishop's people try to locate Kalinda, and Diane, Cary and David's actions make Louis Canning their permanent enemy.    ", season_id: 2556, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-05-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4559048/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Everything Is Ending", episode_number: "S5, Ep1", description: "\nAlicia works on a Death Row appeal with Will and Diane before going off to start her own firm with Cary, but people begin to suspect something is afoot. Meanwhile, Peter searches for a Chief of Staff.    ", season_id: 2557, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-09-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2801442/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The Bit Bucket", episode_number: "S5, Ep2", description: "\nOne of Lockhart Gardner's Internet clients takes on the NSA, Diane's nomination to the Supreme Court hits a snag, and Alicia's mom's \"investment\" could expose Alicia's imminent departure from the firm.    ", season_id: 2557, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3150052/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "A Precious Commodity", episode_number: "S5, Ep3", description: "\nWhile Alicia defends a surrogate mother being forced to abort a baby, she also unwittingly gets thrust into the middle of a struggle by Will to get Diane removed from the firm.    ", season_id: 2557, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3150054/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Outside the Bubble", episode_number: "S5, Ep4", description: "\nAs Diane prepares for big changes as she leaves the firm, the firm faces a politically-motivated sexual harassment suit. Meanwhile, Jackie makes trouble for the inauguration, and Alicia and Cary's departure from the firm is imminent.    ", season_id: 2557, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3163792/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Hitting the Fan", episode_number: "S5, Ep5", description: "\nWhen Will find out that Alicia and Cary are leaving the firm, he fires them and sets out to destroy them before they can get their new firm off the ground.    ", season_id: 2557, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3234826/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The Next Day", episode_number: "S5, Ep6", description: "\nLockhart Gardner and Florrick Agos fight over clients and expert witnesses in a gun case, Diane loses her Illinois Supreme Court nomination, and Alicia faces ethics questions over her husband's actions.    ", season_id: 2557, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3268598/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "The Next Week", episode_number: "S5, Ep7", description: "\nAlicia and Cary suspect the old firm may be spying on them, and they turn to an old face for financial advice. Meanwhile, Alicia may be liable in a multi-million dollar lawsuit against Lockhart Gardner.    ", season_id: 2557, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3283790/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "The Next Month", episode_number: "S5, Ep8", description: "\nAlicia represents an illegal immigrant who faces certain death if he is deported, and Eli gets in trouble when he makes a policy decision for Peter based on his feelings for a woman.    ", season_id: 2557, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3227430/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
