  {title: "VIP Treatment", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nThe firm does some makeshift, last-minute investigating in order to decide whether to defend a masseuse accusing a beloved Nobel Prize winner of sexual assault, but the accused tries to use Peter to sway the firm's decision.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-10-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632300/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Poisoned Pill", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nThe firm takes on a test case which could lead to a class-action suit against a pharmaceutical company, a dirty trick against Wendy Scott-Carr backfires for Florrick and Childs' campaigns, and Blake and Kalinda step up their rivalry.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-11-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632301/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Bad Girls", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nAlicia defends a former teen star against charges of attempted murder. Wendy Scott-Carr launches an all-out assault against Peter's vulnerable campaign, while Peter considers a sweetheart deal to drop out of the race.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-11-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632302/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "On Tap", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nAlicia discovers new information about Eli Gold and Will's feelings while listening to wiretap recordings for a case about a corrupt alderman, and Zach hurts his dad's campaign by producing a viral video.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-11-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632303/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Nine Hours", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nWhile Peter prepares for his debate, Alicia and the rest of the firm work overtime amending a last-minute appeal for a death row inmate after Alicia receives a cryptic call from an appeals court clerk.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-12-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632304/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Breaking Up", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nThe firm tries to get a client's son to turn on his girlfriend when they both face murder charges, Alicia's brother comes for a surprise visit, and Will finds out that Diane is planning to break away from the firm.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-01-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632288/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Two Courts", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nA basketball grudge between Will and a judge could cost Will's client a shot at a fair trial, a new consultant threatens Eli Gold's control over Peter's campaign, and the power plays within the firm become complex and nasty.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-01-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632289/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Silly Season", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nAs Cary and Alicia go head to head again in a prison murder case, Cary uncovers an unlikely connection between the accused and one of Bond's clients. Meanwhile, a dirty campaign trick could backfire on Peter's campaign.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632290/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Real Deal", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nWhile battling an old rival to gain control of a class-action lawsuit, Alicia, Will and Diane discover that a traitor is in their midst. Meanwhile, the Florrick campaign tries to find a way to win the youth vote.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-02-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632291/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Net Worth", episode_number: "S2, Ep14", description: "\nWill and Diane take on a movie studio and screenwriter accused of defamation against a famous computer programmer. Meanwhile, Alicia contemplates her relationship with Will on a cross-country trip, and Blake and Kalinda come to blows.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-02-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632292/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Silver Bullet", episode_number: "S2, Ep15", description: "\nDiane defends her erstwhile love interest, Kurt McVeigh, when he faces a law suit from a convicted criminal who has now been released when his lawyer shows the police and the crime lab manufactured evidence. They go after McVeigh in the belief that he too was part of the conspiracy. To get the case thrown out, Diane will have to show that he made an honest mistake. Meanwhile, Eli Gold thinks he's found the silver bullet in Peter's campaign against Wendy Scott-Carr: it appears that the she hired an illegal alien, Natalie Flores, as a nanny. She's been living in the U.S...    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-02-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632293/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Great Firewall", episode_number: "S2, Ep16", description: "\nAs the vote to determine the fate of the firm arrives, Lockhart, Gardner, and Bond make final maneuvers. Meanwhile, the firm takes a case involving the Internet and human rights, and Peter's campaign tries to take out Glenn Childs.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-03-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632294/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Ham Sandwich", episode_number: "S2, Ep17", description: "\nAlicia helps Bishop with his divorce and custody settlement, and helps Kalinda after she is subpoenaed to appear in front of a grand jury. Meanwhile, Eli changes Peter's campaign strategy to appeal to white, middle-class voters.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-03-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632295/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Killer Song", episode_number: "S2, Ep18", description: "\nThe firm takes a case involving a killer who allegedly wrote a song about his crime, Eli tries to help the family of Wendy Scott-Carr's illegal nanny, and Peter takes steps to keep his and Kalinda's secret from going public.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-03-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632296/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Wrongful Termination", episode_number: "S2, Ep19", description: "\nTo Lockhart/Gardner's disbelief, Louis Canning returns to face off against Alicia once again when the firm represents families of workers who committed suicide due to miserable working conditions. Meanwhile, Cary finds out shocking information about Kalinda.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-04-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1869080/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Foreign Affairs", episode_number: "S2, Ep20", description: "\nOn the eve of the election, Eli tries to persuade Alicia to conduct an interview on behalf of her husband. Meanwhile, Lockhart Gardner is forced to work with Fred Thompson and the Venezuelan government on an oil case.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-04-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1869081/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "In Sickness", episode_number: "S2, Ep21", description: "\nAfter Peter wins the election, Alicia kicks Peter out of the house because of his affair with Kalinda. Meanwhile, opposing counsel in an organ transplant case suddenly asks Will to represent her when her firm fires her.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-05-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1869082/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "Getting Off", episode_number: "S2, Ep22", description: "\nAlicia is assigned to defend a woman who is being sued by a widow whose husband was murdered by someone he met on the defendant's website. Once again, Alicia and Will are up against the somewhat ditsy Nancy Crozier. When her case turns to accusing the defendant of murder - and Carey Agos takes an all too obvious interest in the civil proceedings - Alicia and Will realize they have to change their strategy. At the office, Alicia lays it on the line with Kalinda, who decides to get a job elsewhere.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-05-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1869083/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Closing Arguments", episode_number: "S2, Ep23", description: "\nLockhart Gardner is in a race against time after new evidence in a murder trial is discovered during jury deliberations, Eli Gold offers his consulting services to the firm, and Alicia and Will reevaluate their working relationship.    ", season_id: 2560, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2011-05-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1869084/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "Pilot", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nAlicia Florrick returns to her job as a lawyer after her husband, a prominent state's attorney, is imprisoned. Her first case involves a mother who is facing trial for killing her ex-husband.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-09-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1465795/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Stripped", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nAlicia takes on the second chair of a rape case: a civil suit involving the abuse of a prostitute who may have been hired by her husband.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-09-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1465794/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Home", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nAlicia defends the son of former friends, who have ostracized her since the scandal, on a charge of felony murder.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-10-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1477534/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Fixed", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nAlicia is asked to find evidence that could help her husband get a new trial. Meanwhile, during a class action trial, she suspects that she has found evidence that the defense is paying off a juror.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-10-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1517543/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Crash", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nAlicia and Will represent three widows who are suing the freight train company their husbands worked for after a fatal accident, while Diane asks Kalinda to gather information on a lawyer who may be considered as a new partner.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-10-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1516368/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Conjugal", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nThe firm gets a retrial in a case involving a convicted death row inmate, and Alicia is forced to turn to her husband to get information that will help them win the case.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-11-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1520787/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Unorthodox", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nAfter a young boy is hospitalized for blood loss following a rape, Stabler and Munch focus on a Hasidic order whose reluctance to cooperate may lead the investigation away from the real perpetrator.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2008-01-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1535866/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Unprepared", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nAs Alicia prepares to defend a scientist accused of starting a fire in a university lab, she is asked to testify in her husband's appeal, which could send him home sooner than expected.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-11-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1541471/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Threesome", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nPeter's prostitute goes public with accusations that are very embarrassing to Alicia and her family. Meanwhile, name partner Jonah Stern asks Alicia to help defend him after he is accused of DUI and assaulting a police officer.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-11-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1548489/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Lifeguard", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nWhen a judge overturns a simple plea deal that Alicia arranged, she looks into his motivation, and Diane is made an offer she can't refuse...to Will's delight.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-12-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1565894/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Infamy", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nAlicia is taken off a high-profile First Amendment case involving an obnoxious talk show host who may be responsible for a woman's suicide when the wife of one of her husband's rivals requests her as her divorce lawyer.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-01-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1553771/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Painkiller", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nAlicia defends a doctor accused of prescribing oxycodone to a star high school quarterback who overdosed, provides information to Peter about his rival, Glenn Childs, and deals with Peter's mother, who has suffered a stroke.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-01-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1570315/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Bad", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nAs Peter's trial begins, Alicia is busy with a civil trial defending a contemptible husband who was found not guilty of killing his wife. Meanwhile, Diane considers buying a gun for protection against an ex-con.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-02-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1583696/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Hi", episode_number: "S1, Ep14", description: "\nAs Alicia defends a husband accused of murdering the babysitter, she and her family prepare for the outcome of Peter's appeal and his possible homecoming.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-02-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1588694/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Bang", episode_number: "S1, Ep15", description: "\nPeter returns home and discovers the secret photos that his children have been keeping from Alicia. At Alicia's firm, Will removes her from a case involving a bodyguard accused of killing his boss, a dishonest financial planner.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-03-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1608467/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Fleas", episode_number: "S1, Ep16", description: "\nThe firm is having financial problems, so Will takes on a questionable case and considers taking on an unsavory client. Meanwhile, Alicia tries to find out who's been Tweeting gossip about her relationship with her husband.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-03-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1608468/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Heart", episode_number: "S1, Ep17", description: "\nWill makes a move on Alicia as the firm takes on an insurance company denying coverage for a risky, expensive surgery to an expectant mother. Meanwhile, Peter seeks public reconciliation with the African American community.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-03-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1608469/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Doubt", episode_number: "S1, Ep18", description: "\nWhile a jury deliberates a case involving a co-ed accused of murder, ballistics expert Kurt McVeigh reenters Diane's life, while the awkwardness between Will and Alicia intensifies.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-04-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1609416/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Boom", episode_number: "S1, Ep19", description: "\nStern launches his plan to take down Lockhart and Gardner and steal all their best lawyers, while a potential surprise witness emerges with dirt against Peter.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-04-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1641358/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Mock", episode_number: "S1, Ep20", description: "\nAlicia tries to help an Indian family in her building after the mom faces deportation unless the son helps the feds bring down a group of smugglers, while Will presides as the judge in a law school mock trial.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-05-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1641359/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Unplugged", episode_number: "S1, Ep21", description: "\nWhile the firm takes on a case involving a divorce settlement for the wife of a musician who is in a coma, Alicia reluctantly considers a bold move to make sure that Lockhart and Gardner choose her over Cary.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-05-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1644990/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "Hybristophilia", episode_number: "S1, Ep22", description: "\nWill sends Alicia to disgraced CEO Colin Sweeney's home to handle merger details, but finds him with a dead body instead. Meanwhile, Glen Childs tries to save his case against Peter, and Cary searches for a way to get back at Alicia.    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-05-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1644964/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Running", episode_number: "S1, Ep23", description: "\nThe firm goes head-to-head with Cary and other familiar faces in a police corruption case. Meanwhile, Eli Gold seeks to put pressure on Peter to run for reelection, but will Alicia go along for the ride?    ", season_id: 2561, series_id: 41, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2010-05-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt1632305/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
