  {title: "The One with the Baby Shower", episode_number: "S8, Ep20", description: "\nMonica and Phoebe throw Rachel a baby shower and forget to invite Rachel's mom. Rachel realizes she has no idea how to look after the baby after the birth. Meanwhile, Joey auditions for a job as a host for a new game show called \"Bamboozled\" and Chandler and Ross help him practice.    ", season_id: 2574, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2002-04-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583573/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "The One with the Cooking Class", episode_number: "S8, Ep21", description: "\nMonica's restaurant get a bad review. After confronting the critic who wrote it, she decides to join a cooking class, with Joey in tow. Rachel gets jealous when Ross hits it off with a woman at the baby department store.    ", season_id: 2574, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2002-05-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583592/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "The One Where Rachel Is Late", episode_number: "S8, Ep22", description: "\nRachel becomes extremely irritable when her pregnancy is overdue by eight days, which leads to a bet between Monica and Phoebe. Meanwhile, Joey invites Chander to the screening of his new movie.    ", season_id: 2574, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2002-05-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583473/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "The One Where Rachel Has a Baby: Part 1", episode_number: "S8, Ep23", description: "\nRoss and Rachel go to the hospital to have their baby but it's a long labor. They get stuck in a semi-private room and many other couples come and go before Rachel is ready to deliver, the last couple being Janice and her new husband. Chandler and Monica decide to start trying to have a baby.    ", season_id: 2574, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2002-05-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583471/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "The One Where Rachel Has a Baby: Part 2", episode_number: "S8, Ep24", description: "\nAfter 21 hours Rachel is finally ready to go to the delivery room and baby-girl Geller Green is born and her name is Emma! Janice comes to see Rachel and Janice says she admires Rachel for her strength to raise the child on her own. When Rachel says she isn't alone because she has Ross, Janice tells her that Ross won't stay around forever and might meet someone else. Suddenly, Rachel feels very alone and she tries to talk to Ross about the kiss they had. Ross doesn't want to have a relationship with Rachel anymore because if it doesn't work out it would really hurt ...    ", season_id: 2574, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2002-05-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583472/?ref_=ttep_ep24"},
  {title: "The One with Monica's Thunder", episode_number: "S7, Ep1", description: "\nThe gang celebrate Monica and Chandler's engagement, however Ross and Rachel upstage them by briefly reuniting.    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-10-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0756483/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The One with Rachel's Book", episode_number: "S7, Ep2", description: "\nMonica learns her parents have spent her entire wedding fund. Phoebe temporarily moves into Ross's apartment, bringing her massage clients with her. Joey mocks Rachel when he finds an erotic novel she is reading.    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-10-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583546/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "The One with Phoebe's Cookies", episode_number: "S7, Ep3", description: "\nMonica tries to figure out Phoebe's grandmother's secret cookie recipe. Meanwhile, Rachel tries to teach Joey how to sail, and Chandler has an awkward encounter when he tries to bond with Jack.    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-10-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583536/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "The One with Rachel's Assistant", episode_number: "S7, Ep4", description: "\nChaos ensues when Monica and Chandler decide to share each other's secrets. Rachel gets a promotion and interviews for an assistant. Joey is offered the chance to go back on \"Days of our Lives\".    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-10-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583544/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "The One with the Engagement Picture", episode_number: "S7, Ep5", description: "\nChandler struggles to photograph well for his and Monica's engagement picture. Joey teaches Tag how to pick up women, much to Rachel's annoyance. Phoebe and Ross date a couple who are divorcing.    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-11-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583601/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The One with the Nap Partners", episode_number: "S7, Ep6", description: "\nJoey and Ross accidentally take a nap together and much to their dismay, find that they like it. Phoebe and Rachel compete to become Monica's maid of honor.    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-11-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583632/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "The One with Ross's Library Book", episode_number: "S7, Ep7", description: "\nMonica runs into Janice and Janice is shocked to hear that she is getting married to Chandler but invites herself and her boyfriend to the wedding. Ross' doctoral dissertation can be found at the library but when he goes to see it he finds out that the Palaentology section of the library is only used when students make out together. Therefore Ross decides to defend the area. Rachel and Phoebe find the perfect girl for Joey and he is really into her but she doesn't feel the same way. Chandler and Monica can finally get rid of Janice.    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-11-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583558/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "The One Where Chandler Doesn't Like Dogs", episode_number: "S7, Ep8", description: "\nIt's Thanksgiving and the friends and Tag are preparing for dinner. Phoebe secretly keeps a dog she is watching for friends who went out of town in her room at Monica and Chandler's apartment. Everybody thought Chandler was allergic to dogs but the truth is that he hates dogs because he scared of them because you can never tell what they're thinking. Tag broke up with his girlfriend and Rachel is thinking about making a move. When Rachel tells Tag that she likes him he doesn't reply because he sees his car being stolen. Later on Rachel says he should just forget about...    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-11-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583431/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The One with All the Candy", episode_number: "S7, Ep9", description: "\nMonica makes candy for their neighbours even though they don't know them. The neighbours love the candy and Monica becomes very popular in the building. Rachel and Tag try to hide their relationship at work but when Rachel writes a revealing evaluation as a joke and Tag sends it on to human resources without reading it, they have a problem. Ross finds out that Phoebe never owned a bike so he buys her the prettiest pink bike there is and teaches Phoebe how to ride. Tag and Rachel almost get fired but manage to solve the problem. TOns of people hang around the apartment...    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-12-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583503/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The One with the Holiday Armadillo", episode_number: "S7, Ep10", description: "\nRoss wants to introduce Ben to Chanukah. In order to entice Rachel to move back into their refurbished apartment, Pheobe must drive a wedge between Rachel and current roomie Joey.    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2000-12-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583613/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "The One with All the Cheesecakes", episode_number: "S7, Ep11", description: "\nChandler and Rachel eat a cheesecake that was accidentally delivered to their door and it's the best cheesecake they've ever had. Another cheesecake gets delivered and they try to resist and drop it off to their neighbour that was supposed to receive it. Ross is invited to a cousin's wedding but Monica isn't. Monica is very upset because she was the girl's best friend when they grew up together so she gets Ross to take her instead of a date. Rachel and Chandler find the cheesecake untouched in front of the neighbour's door so they take it. Monica wasn't invited to the...    ", season_id: 2575, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2001-01-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583504/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
