  {title: "The One Without the Ski Trip", episode_number: "S3, Ep17", description: "\nWhen Ross rescues the group after they've become stranded on the way to a ski trip he wasn't invited on, the rest of the gang are forced to address the hostility between him and Rachel after their split.    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-03-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583495/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "The One with the Hypnosis Tape", episode_number: "S3, Ep18", description: "\nMonica goes out with a guy who turns out to be a software billionaire. Chandler's stop smoking hypnosis tape has an unexpected side effect. Frank makes a surprise announcement that he is getting married - to a woman twice his age.    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-03-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583615/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "The One with the Tiny T-Shirt", episode_number: "S3, Ep19", description: "\nRachel goes on her first date after splitting from Ross, with Mark. Joey clashes with his co-star in his new play. Monica continues to date Pete, even though she is still not attracted to him.    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-03-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583654/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "The One with the Dollhouse", episode_number: "S3, Ep20", description: "\nKate is the first woman Joey liked who doesn't like him back. Monica's and Ross' aunt Sylvia died and Monica inherits the dollhouse with which she was never allowed to play. Monica invites Phoebe to play with the dollhouse but doesn't let her play anymore when Phoebe brings out a dinosaur, a giant dog and a ghost. Phoebe makes her own dollhouse which is way cooler than Monica's. Chandler has a date with Rachel's boss Joanna and finds her really dull and boring. Joanna thinks they have chemistry and loves Rachel for introducing her to Chandler. Joey and Kate are ...    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-04-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583596/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "The One with the Chick and the Duck", episode_number: "S3, Ep21", description: "\nJoey buys a chick for him and Chandler, Pete offers Monica a job at his restaurant, and Ross gives up being on TV for Rachel.    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-04-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583590/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "The One with the Screamer", episode_number: "S3, Ep22", description: "\nRoss witnesses Rachel's date screaming at people, however no one believes him. Meanwhile, Joey becomes upset when Kate is offered a job in Los Angeles, and Phoebe refuses to hang up the phone when she is placed on hold by her phone company.    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-04-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583643/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "The One with Ross's Thing", episode_number: "S3, Ep23", description: "\nRoss seeks medical help when he finds a mysterious skin condition on his behind. Phoebe struggles to choose between two guys. Monica can't decide what to do about Pete when she thinks he is going to propose.    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-05-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583565/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "The One with the Ultimate Fighting Champion", episode_number: "S3, Ep24", description: "\nMonica struggles to support Pete in his goal to become the Ultimate Fighting Champion. Chandler is unnerved when his boss slaps his butt. Rachel becomes jealous when Ross starts dating a new woman.    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-05-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583657/?ref_=ttep_ep24"},
  {title: "The One at the Beach", episode_number: "S3, Ep25", description: "\nThe gang go to the beach to learn more about Phoebe's family, where a jealous Rachel sabotages Ross and Bonnie's relationship.    ", season_id: 2579, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1997-05-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583496/?ref_=ttep_ep25"},
  {title: "The One with Ross's New Girlfriend", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nRachel waits for Ross at the airport, unaware he has a new girlfriend. Meanwhile, Chandler has a frightening experience with Joey's tailor, and Phoebe gives Monica a bad haircut.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-09-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583562/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The One with the Breast Milk", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nMonica goes shopping with Julie and tries to keep it a secret from Rachel. Ross is grossed out by Carol's breast milk. At his day job, Joey competes with a fellow cologne spritzer.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-09-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583583/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "The One Where Heckles Dies", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nAfter Mr. Heckles dies and leaves all his belongings to Monica and Rachel, Chandler worries he will die alone just like him. Meanwhile, Phoebe and Ross argue over evolution.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-10-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583453/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "The One with Phoebe's Husband", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nWhen the gang find out Phoebe married a gay Canadian ice dancer for a green card, more of their secrets are revealed. Meanwhile, Rachel gives Ross bad advice on his relationship with Julie.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-10-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583539/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "The One with Five Steaks and an Eggplant", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nThe gang are divided by income issues; Monica, Ross and Chandler have money, and Rachel, Phoebe and Joey don't.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-10-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583519/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The One with the Baby on the Bus", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nJoey and Chandler are left to babysit Ben when Monica takes Ross to the hospital. Meanwhile, Phoebe loses her singing gig at Central Perk to a professional singer.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-11-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583574/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "The One Where Ross Finds Out", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nA drunken Rachel calls Ross and reveals her feelings for him on his answering machine. Meanwhile, Monica finds work as Chandler's personal trainer.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-11-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583481/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "The One with the List", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nRoss makes a list of pros and cons to decide whether to be with Julie or Rachel. Meanwhile, Monica gets a job making food with a disgusting synthetic chocolate substitute.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-11-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583625/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The One with Phoebe's Dad", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nPhoebe tracks down her father, but isn't sure whether she should meet him. Ross asks Rachel to make a list of pros and cons about him.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-12-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583537/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The One with Russ", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nMonica gets back together with 'Fun Bobby' and realizes why he is always so upbeat. Rachel starts dating a guy called Russ who bears an uncanny resemblance to Ross.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-01-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583567/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "The One with the Lesbian Wedding", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nRachel's mom comes to visit with big news. Monica caters Carol and Susan's wedding. Phoebe becomes 'possessed' by the spirit of a recently deceased client.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-01-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583624/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "The One After the Superbowl: Part 1", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nRoss goes to visit Marcel whilst on a trip to California and discovers he is working in commercials. Joey receives a fan letter from an attractive but unstable woman. Phoebe is asked to sing for children at a library.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-01-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583439/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "The One After the Superbowl: Part 2", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nRoss finds Marcel on the set of a new movie, where Chandler bumps into a former schoolmate. Meanwhile, Rachel and Monica compete for the affections of Jean-Claude Van Damme.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-01-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0831047/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "The One with the Prom Video", episode_number: "S2, Ep14", description: "\nThe gang watch a home video from the night of Monica and Rachel's prom. Joey gives Chandler a hideous bracelet.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-02-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583635/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "The One Where Ross and Rachel... You Know", episode_number: "S2, Ep15", description: "\nMonica becomes infatuated with a friend of her parents when she caters a party for him. Ross and Rachel go on their first date. Joey and Chandler refuse to move when they get a new TV and two armchairs.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-02-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583488/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "The One Where Joey Moves Out", episode_number: "S2, Ep16", description: "\nJoey and Chandler's friendship is jeopardized when Joey decides to move out. Monica worries about her parents finding out about her relationship with Richard when they attend a party together. Rachel and Phoebe go to get tattoos.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-02-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583456/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "The One Where Eddie Moves In", episode_number: "S2, Ep17", description: "\nJoey shows the friends his new apartment. Chandler and Joey miss each other and watch Baywatch in their apartments while talking on the phone together. Phoebe gets a chance to record \"Smelly Cat\" but can't cope with the background singers. Ross is driving Monica crazy because he is so much at Monica's and Rachel's place Monica feels like 16 again living with her brother. Chandler finds a new roommate called Eddie. Chandler is shocked to find that Eddie doesn't like foosball nor Baywatch...    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-02-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583448/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "The One Where Dr. Ramoray Dies", episode_number: "S2, Ep18", description: "\nChandler finds out Eddy is not only much less fun then Joey, but positively crazy and frighteningly suspicious and inconsistent. Ross is stressing out to learn Rachel has 'animal sex' with Paolo; Richard and Monica are uncomfortable to learn she is only his second lover, he the last in a long row; there's a logistical dilemma for both couples' make up-sex. After Joey told a TV digest he 'rewrites some of his dialogs', an insulted scenarist writes his character Dr. Drake Ramoray to fall to his death, ending his DOOL-career.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-03-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583447/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "The One Where Eddie Won't Go", episode_number: "S2, Ep19", description: "\nChandler demands that Eddie move out, however he doesn't seem to get the message. Meanwhile, a book on empowerment for women inspires the girls.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-03-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583449/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "The One Where Old Yeller Dies", episode_number: "S2, Ep20", description: "\nPhoebe's world view is shattered when she learns how Old Yeller really ends. Monica becomes jealous when Richard starts hanging out with Chandler and Joey. Rachel panics when she learns that Ross has planned their whole life together.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-04-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583465/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "The One with the Bullies", episode_number: "S2, Ep21", description: "\nChandler and Ross run into two bullies at Central Perk. Monica tries her luck at the stock market to avoid taking a job at a tacky 1950s themed diner. Phoebe drives upstate for a second time to meet her father.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-04-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583584/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "The One with the Two Parties", episode_number: "S2, Ep22", description: "\nChaos ensues when Rachel's recently divorced parents show up at her surprise birthday party.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-05-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583656/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "The One with the Chicken Pox", episode_number: "S2, Ep23", description: "\nPhoebe catches chicken pox just as an old flame arrives in town on leave from the Navy. Joey gets a job at Chandler's office. Monica is upset that Richard doesn't have any quirks.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-05-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583591/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "The One with Barry and Mindy's Wedding", episode_number: "S2, Ep24", description: "\nRachel reluctantly agrees to be maid of honor at her ex-fiancé Barry's wedding. Monica ponders her future with Richard. Joey tries to practice kissing guys to get a role in Warren Beatty's new movie.    ", season_id: 2580, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1996-05-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583514/?ref_=ttep_ep24"},
  {title: "The One Where Monica Gets a Roommate", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nMonica and the gang introduce Rachel to the \"real world\" after she leaves her fiancé at the altar.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-09-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583459/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The One with the Sonogram at the End", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nRoss finds out his ex-wife is pregnant. Rachel returns her engagement ring to Barry. Monica becomes stressed when her and Ross's parents come to visit.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-09-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583647/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "The One with the Thumb", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nMonica becomes irritated when everyone likes her new boyfriend more than she does. Chandler resumes his smoking habit. Phoebe is given $7000 when she finds a thumb in a can of soda.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-10-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583653/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "The One with George Stephanopoulos", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nJoey and Chandler take Ross to a hockey game to take his mind off the anniversary of the first time he slept with Carol, while the girls become depressed when they realize they don't have a 'plan'.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-10-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583521/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "The One with the East German Laundry Detergent", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nEager to spend time with Rachel, Ross pretends his washroom is rat-infested so he can join her at the laundromat. Meanwhile, Joey has Monica pose as his girlfriend, and Chandler struggles to break up with his girlfriend.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-10-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583599/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The One with the Butt", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nMonica's obsessiveness is put to the test after Rachel cleans the apartment. Joey lands a film role as Al Pacino's butt double. Chandler enjoys a relationship with all of the fun but none of the responsibility.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-10-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583585/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "The One with the Blackout", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nWhen New York suffers from a blackout, Ross tries to tell Rachel that he likes her, and Chandler gets stuck in an ATM vestibule with a model.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-11-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583579/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "The One Where Nana Dies Twice", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nMonica and Ross mourn the loss of their grandmother. Chandler is shocked to find that people think he is gay.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-11-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583462/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The One Where Underdog Gets Away", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nThe gang's plans for Thanksgiving go awry after they get locked out of Monica and Rachel's apartment.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-11-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583492/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The One with the Monkey", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nThe gang make (and break) a pact not to bring dates to their New Years Eve party. Phoebe starts dating a scientist. Ross compensates for his loneliness by getting a monkey.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1994-12-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583630/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "The One with Mrs. Bing", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nChandler's flamboyant romance-novelist mother comes to visit, and Joey catches her kissing Ross. Meanwhile, Monica and Phoebe fight over a guy in a coma.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-01-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583534/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "The One with the Dozen Lasagnas", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nRachel and Paolo's relationship hits a snag after he gropes Phoebe. Ross has a hard time not knowing the sex of his and Carol's baby. Joey and Chandler get a foosball table.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-01-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583598/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "The One with the Boobies", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nJoey finds out his dad has a mistress. Rachel tries to even the score after Chandler inadvertently catches a glimpse of her breasts. Phoebe dates a shrink who analyzes the gang.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-01-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583582/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "The One with the Candy Hearts", episode_number: "S1, Ep14", description: "\nAs Valentine's Day approaches; Ross and his date end up at the same restaurant as Carol and Susan, Joey inadvertently sets Chandler up on a blind date with Janice, and the girls burn mementos of their old boyfriends.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-02-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583587/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "The One with the Stoned Guy", episode_number: "S1, Ep15", description: "\nMonica cooks a gourmet meal for a restaurateur who is looking for a new chef, however he arrives at the apartment stoned. Meanwhile, Ross tries to master 'dirty talk'.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-02-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583649/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "The One with Two Parts: Part 1", episode_number: "S1, Ep16", description: "\nPhoebe feels neglected when Joey falls for her twin sister. Chandler struggles to fire an attractive co-worker. Ross attends Lamaze classes with Carol and Susan.    ", season_id: 2581, series_id: 43, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "1995-02-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt0583568/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
