  {title: "All My Exes Live in Essex", episode_number: "S4, Ep4", description: "\nWhen Holmes and Watson investigate the murder of a fertility lab technician, they discover the woman had a secret personal life that leads them to multiple suspects. Also, the tables are turned on Watson when she's investigated by an NYPD detective.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-11-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4962286/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "The Games Underfoot", episode_number: "S4, Ep5", description: "\nSherlock and Joan investigate the murder of a struggling archaeologist who was seemingly killed for some vintage video games he unearthed.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-12-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5205008/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The Cost of Doing Business", episode_number: "S4, Ep6", description: "\nMorland offers to act as one of his son's \"Irregular\" consultants so that he can lend Sherlock and Joan his considerable resources to help them solve a case.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-12-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5128632/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Miss Taken", episode_number: "S4, Ep7", description: "\nThe duo goes against a clever opponent, who forces Holmes to think out of the box. Meanwhile Watson's troubles with her father are brought into focus when he writes a book about her and Holmes.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5266828/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "A Burden of Blood", episode_number: "S4, Ep8", description: "\nSherlock thinks Watson and Det. Bell are having an affair. A series of apparently connected events occur after a murder which forces the detective to question his own theory at every step.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5189500/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Murder Ex Machina", episode_number: "S4, Ep9", description: "\nA Russian billionaire is assassinated in New York and Holmes and Watson embark upon several instances of hacking and weaponory business. Meanwhile, a secret about Morland, Sherlock's father is revealed.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5104934/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Alma Matters", episode_number: "S4, Ep10", description: "\nA social worker asks Holmes and Watson to investigate a private college, when she becomes convinced that they have murdered one of her colleagues.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-01-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5329102/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Down Where the Dead Delight", episode_number: "S4, Ep11", description: "\nWhen evidence at the morgue is destroyed, suspicion falls on emerging gangs. Holmes believes that identifying a Jane Doe will help him unlock the case, while Watson deals with the reappearance of an old adversary.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5235370/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "A View with a Room", episode_number: "S4, Ep12", description: "\nSherlock is recruited to heist a computer from a violent meth dealing motorcycle gang. While a former suspect from a previous case asks Joan to run a background check on her new boss.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5301312/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "A Study in Charlotte", episode_number: "S4, Ep13", description: "\nWhen a gathering of mushroom aficionados are found dead, Holmes and Watson must explore an array of botanists, biochemists, academics and stoners for a poisoner.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5264246/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Who Is That Masked Man?", episode_number: "S4, Ep14", description: "\nHolmes investigates the assassination attempt on his father while trying to solve the triple homocide of Chinese gangsters. A secret about Sherlock's mother is revealed.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-02-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5280540/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Up to Heaven and Down to Hell", episode_number: "S4, Ep15", description: "\nWhen Watson runs into Captain Gregson and his secret girlfriend, a former NYPD officer, she inadvertently sets the couple's breakup in motion. Also, Holmes and Watson investigate the murder of a wealthy woman who left her considerable estate solely to a beloved dog.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5378252/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Hounded", episode_number: "S4, Ep16", description: "\nAt the urging of Morland's wealthy associate, Henry Baskerville (Tom Everett Scott), Holmes and Watson look into the death of his brother and discover that a witness saw the man chased to his death by a large, glowing animal too fantastic to be real. Sherlock considers intervening when the trauma from the bombing at the morgue negatively impacts ME Hawes' work.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5361182/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "You've Got Me, Who's Got You?", episode_number: "S4, Ep17", description: "\nWhen a vigilante dressed as a comic book hero is murdered, it's up to Holmes and Watson to find the man's true identity and locate his killer; Moreland tries to charm Watson into doing him a favor.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5527116/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Ready or Not", episode_number: "S4, Ep18", description: "\nHolmes and Watson are called in to help locate a missing doctor. It is unclear at first whether he has gone into hiding or is a victim of foul play. Holmes and Fiona's relationship takes a new turn.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5457782/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "All In", episode_number: "S4, Ep19", description: "\nHolmes and Watson investigate a burglary at an illegal high stakes poker game held by Mycroft's ex girlfriend. Watson is suspicious of their employer.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5489970/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Art Imitates Art", episode_number: "S4, Ep20", description: "\nHolmes and Watson investigate the murder of a young woman whose college selfie was turned into a piece of contemporary art. Watson tries to get closer to her half-sister.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5568944/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Ain't Nothing Like the Real Thing", episode_number: "S4, Ep21", description: "\nWhen Holmes and Watson are pulled into a double-homicide investigation, they discover the victims were staging a fake murder right at the moment they were killed. Also, Watson's inside man at Morland's office encounters a problem that threatens to expose her spying to Holmes and his father.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5568946/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "Turn It Upside Down", episode_number: "S4, Ep22", description: "\nSherlock's father, Morland (John Noble), becomes Sherlock and Joan's prime suspect in a murder investigation after one of his employees is killed under the guise of a robbery.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5588866/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "The Invisible Hand", episode_number: "S4, Ep23", description: "\nSherlock's suspicions concerning Moriarty's handiwork turn out to be true and her evil successor is revealed. Morland's desire for vengeance causes Sherlock to consider just which brand of justice this new villain warrants.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5622962/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "A Difference in Kind", episode_number: "S4, Ep24", description: "\nVikner's diabolical maneuvering to secure his position becomes known. Sherlock concocts a plan to unseat him only to unwittingly enable a power struggle the ends of which he could barely have believed possible.    ", season_id: 2586, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5680670/?ref_=ttep_ep24"},
  {title: "Enough Nemesis to Go Around", episode_number: "S3, Ep1", description: "\nHolmes returns to New York with a new apprentice and a renewed interest in working with the NYPD after being fired by London's MI6. Unfortunately, Joan, the NYPD's new go-to PI, must give her approval first.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-10-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3596108/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The Five Orange Pipz", episode_number: "S3, Ep2", description: "\nWhen Holmes and Watson join forces on a double homicide, Sherlock's new apprentice, Kitty, threatens the investigation when she allows her jealousy of Sherlock and Joan's work rapport to override her better judgment.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4038658/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Just a Regular Irregular", episode_number: "S3, Ep3", description: "\nSherlock helps a math genius from his network of \"Irregulars\" experts after he stumbles upon a body while participating in a math puzzle competition. Meanwhile, Joan attempts to extend an olive branch after she learns about Kitty's past.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4166616/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Bella", episode_number: "S3, Ep4", description: "\nAn A.I. computer is suspected for the murder of its creator; Sherlock and the team go to work to solve the case.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4109322/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Rip Off", episode_number: "S3, Ep5", description: "\nSherlock and Kitty investigate after a man's severed hand is found in the street; Gregson gets in trouble with the brass and his daughter when he punches another cop; Sherlock discovers a manuscript that Watson has written about his cases.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-11-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4188090/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Terra Pericolosa", episode_number: "S3, Ep6", description: "\nHolmes and Watson search for a thief who committed murder to steal a rare map. Meanwhile, Watson becomes concerned with Sherlock's escalating interference into Kitty's burgeoning personal life. Mamie Gummer guest stars.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-12-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4193778/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "The Adventure of the Nutmeg Concoction", episode_number: "S3, Ep7", description: "\nA bored Sherlock forces his investigative services onto Joan, who is trying to locate a woman who has been missing for five years, and the only clue is the smell of nutmeg at the site of her disappearance. Meanwhile, Joan's bond with her long-distance boyfriend, Andrew, is tested when a man from her past reappears and asks for her help.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-12-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4132718/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "End of Watch", episode_number: "S3, Ep8", description: "\nHolmes and Watson join forces with the NYPD after a police officer is murdered. Also, Sherlock searches for the creator of a \"recovery blog\" who is posting personal statements he has made in sobriety meetings.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-12-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4259236/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The Eternity Injection", episode_number: "S3, Ep9", description: "\nWhen a nurse Watson used to work with asks for her help finding their missing acquaintance, the woman's trail leads Watson and Holmes to another person who has disappeared. Also, Sherlock struggles with his sobriety when he finds the recovery process monotonous.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4165846/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Seed Money", episode_number: "S3, Ep10", description: "\nWhile Kitty tries to find a runaway teen, Sherlock and Joan work a case in which the murder of a brilliant bioengineer looks to be at the hands of a drug cartel. Also, Joan makes a major life decision but worries it will impact Sherlock negatively, not knowing that Sherlock has big news of his own.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4300564/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "The Illustrious Client", episode_number: "S3, Ep11", description: "\nWatson starts her new job as an investigator for an insurance firm, but ends up joining forces on a case with Sherlock when a threat to Kitty emerges.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4300570/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "The One That Got Away", episode_number: "S3, Ep12", description: "\nAs Kitty begins to unravel due to the imminent threat to her safety, Sherlock and Joan intensify their efforts to help her. Also, the origin of Sherlock and Kitty's relationship is revealed.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4214936/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Hemlock", episode_number: "S3, Ep13", description: "\nHolmes and Watson are faced with a very large suspect pool when a debt collector is murdered; Andrew wants Watson to meet his father.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4389654/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "The Female of the Species", episode_number: "S3, Ep14", description: "\nSherlock and Detective Bell investigate the kidnapping of two zebras from the zoo.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4389658/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "When Your Number's Up", episode_number: "S3, Ep15", description: "\nHolmes and Watson follow a blood trail into the world of wrongful death compensation when they investigate a series of murders in which the killer leaves envelopes of cash on the victims. Also, Holmes makes a generous gesture towards Watson as she suffers through the aftermath of a personal crisis.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4331982/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "For All You Know", episode_number: "S3, Ep16", description: "\nHolmes investigates himself when he becomes a suspect in a murder that took place during the height of his addiction; clues make Holmes question his innocence.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4454588/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "T-Bone and the Iceman", episode_number: "S3, Ep17", description: "\nA murder victim turns out to have been instantly frozen at the time of death; Watson is forced to have an awkward conversation with her brother after learning he is having an affair.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4472348/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "The View from Olympus", episode_number: "S3, Ep18", description: "\nA driver for a ride sharing company is intentionally run over by a city cab, Sherlock and Joan wonder if it's a case of professional jealousy. A romance Sherlock has with a longtime Irregular complicates when she makes a shocking request.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4525072/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "One Watson, One Holmes", episode_number: "S3, Ep19", description: "\nHolmes and Watson are drawn into an Internet war when a member of the everyone hacker group is murdered.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4483404/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "A Stitch in Time", episode_number: "S3, Ep20", description: "\nHolmes and Watson investigate the murder of a professional skeptic, a man who debunked paranormal, religious and scientific phenomenon for a living. The case becomes urgent when his homicide reveals a potential threat to homeland security. Also, Captain Gregson's daughter and fellow NYPD officer, Hannah (Liza J. Bennett), asks Watson for help with one of her cases.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4532492/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "Under My Skin", episode_number: "S3, Ep21", description: "\nTwo New York City paramedics are shot and their ambulance with its patient is abducted by the murderer. Holmes and Watson join the manhunt to find out what happened and why. Holmes learns information about Alfredo, which strains their relationship.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4562958/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "The Best Way Out Is Always Through", episode_number: "S3, Ep22", description: "\nWhen a judge is murdered, Holmes and Watson become involved in the interstate search to find the prime suspect, an escaped convict from a privatized prison. Also, when Holmes applies his deductive reasoning to Detective Bell's new relationship, the romance hits a rough patch.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4599456/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Absconded", episode_number: "S3, Ep23", description: "\nA researcher - one of Sherlock's fellow beekeepers - who was investigating a deadly honeybee outbreak is killed; Capt. Gregson asks Watson for help with an unofficial investigation that helps him make a decision.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-05-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4599458/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "A Controlled Descent", episode_number: "S3, Ep24", description: "\nHolmes and Watson take on an investigation of a personal nature when Holmes' friend and former recovery sponsor Alfredo suddenly disappears.    ", season_id: 2587, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-05-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4599460/?ref_=ttep_ep24"},
  {title: "Step Nine", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nHolmes and Watson travel to London to help track down an old mentor and investigate an unsolved mystery. Rhys Ifans guest stars.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-09-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2801436/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Solve for X", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nWhen a well-respected mathematician is found dead, Holmes and Watson set out to solve a murder and the purpose of the highly guarded equation he was trying to decipher.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3125780/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "We Are Everyone", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nWhen Holmes and Watson set out to track down a civil contractor who leaked classified information, their lives are disrupted when they are targeted by the group of cyber-activists protecting him. Tony Award Winner Steve Kazee guest stars.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3093706/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Poison Pen", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nA dominatrix finds her client dead in S&M gear. When poison is revealed to be the cause of death, the nanny becomes a suspect.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3182700/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Ancient History", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nHolmes and Watson find themselves digging through the dark world of the mob to find a killer when they discover the body of a former assassin.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3255194/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "An Unnatural Arrangement", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nCaptain Gregson's team learns a bit about his personal life after his home is invaded. Holmes and Watson track the gunman.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-10-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3182708/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "The Marchioness", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nSherlock's brother, Mycroft, arrives in New York and enlists Holmes and Watson to help solve a case involving his former fiancee. Meanwhile, Sherlock has a difficult time accepting Mycroft and Joan's relationship. Rhys Ifans guest stars.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3182732/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Blood Is Thicker", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nWhen a beautiful young woman is murdered, Holmes and Watson investigate her ties to a billionaire CEO. Meanwhile, Mycroft makes a case for Sherlock to move back to London.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3295662/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "On the Line", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nHolmes and Watson uncover the identity of a serial killer whose case has gone cold and find themselves butting heads with the NYPD.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-11-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3317624/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Tremors", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nWhen an investigation goes horribly wrong, Sherlock must testify in an official police inquiry which jeopardizes his and Watson's future with the NYPD.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-12-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3347990/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Internal Audit", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nWhen a hedge fund manager who was also running a Ponzi scheme is murdered, Holmes and Watson must determine which of his clients is guilty. Also, Sherlock contemplates sponsoring a fellow recovering addict.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-12-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3357010/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "The Diabolical Kind", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nHolmes and Watson come face to face with Moriarty when their one-time adversary is brought in as a consultant on a kidnapping case. Meanwhile, Detective Bell continues his struggle on the road to recovery. Natalie Dormer Returns as Moriarty.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3392730/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "All in the Family", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nWhen a body is found in a barrel, Holmes and Watson launch an investigation into the mafia's ties to the murder. Meanwhile, Sherlock attempts to make amends with Detective Bell. Peter Gerety and Paul Sorvino guest star.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3415320/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Dead Clade Walking", episode_number: "S2, Ep14", description: "\nWhen Joan revisits one of Sherlock's cold cases, she discovers an unsolved murder is connected to a rare prehistoric fossil. Meanwhile, Sherlock finds himself in uncharted territory when his duties as a sobriety sponsor cross his personal boundaries.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-01-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3459420/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "Corpse De Ballet", episode_number: "S2, Ep15", description: "\nHolmes' latest investigation takes him inside a professional dance company when an up-and-coming ballerina is murdered. Meanwhile, Watson embarks on a solo enquiry to find a homeless veteran when his friend alleges he was abducted.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3479240/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "The One Percent Solution", episode_number: "S2, Ep16", description: "\nTensions rise when Holmes and Watson are forced to partner with Gareth Lestrade, Sherlock's former Scotland Yard colleague, on a bombing investigation.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3505070/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Ears to You", episode_number: "S2, Ep17", description: "\nHolmes and Watson consult on a case in which a man suspected of murdering his wife years ago receives a ransom demand for her safe return. Meanwhile, Lestrade overstays his welcome at the brownstone and seems unwilling to leave.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3505072/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "The Hound of the Cancer Cells", episode_number: "S2, Ep18", description: "\nWhen a famous cancer researcher is found dead, Holmes and Watson must determine if the scientist's untimely demise was tied to his latest cutting-edge invention. Meanwhile, Bell is finally cleared to re-enter the field.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3505076/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "The Many Mouths of Andrew Colville", episode_number: "S2, Ep19", description: "\nA serial killer known for biting his victims appears to be killing again, even though he was presumed dead.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3575976/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "No Lack of Void", episode_number: "S2, Ep20", description: "\nHolmes and Watson must find the source of anthrax that may be used for a terrorist attack.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3602686/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "The Man with the Twisted Lip", episode_number: "S2, Ep21", description: "\nWhen Sherlock's brother Mycroft makes a surprise return to New York, his motivations cause discord between Sherlock and Joan. Meanwhile, a missing person case takes Sherlock and Joan inside the world of unmanned aeronautics.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3602688/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "Paint It Black", episode_number: "S2, Ep22", description: "\nWith Watson kidnapped, the Holmes brothers are extorted to buy her back by acquiring something the gangsters greatly value. As the clock runs down on Watson's life, Sherlock is forced to work with his despised brother Mycroft.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3668096/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "Art in the Blood", episode_number: "S2, Ep23", description: "\nMycroft's handler at MI6 asks Sherlock to investigate the death of a mentally disturbed operative. Watson tries to cope with her feelings about the kidnapping, as well as Mycroft's deceptions.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3668094/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "The Grand Experiment", episode_number: "S2, Ep24", description: "\nRising tension between Sherlock and Watson bring their partnership to a crossroads, but they endeavor to put their differences aside while they help Sherlock's brother, Mycroft, who faces accusations of treason and murder. Rhys Ifans returns as Mycroft Holmes.    ", season_id: 2588, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3611988/?ref_=ttep_ep24"},
  {title: "Pilot", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nSherlock Holmes, fresh out of rehab, is teamed with a sobriety partner, a former surgeon named Watson. They have to learn to work together even as they tackle their first case, the mysterious death of a doctor's wife.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-09-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2312764/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "While You Were Sleeping", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nTwo heirs of a fortune are murder suspects, but one sister has an undeniable alibi and the other is a coma patient. Holmes is baffled as to how a coma patient could be the killer until another addict in his support group gives him an idea.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-10-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2331654/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Child Predator", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nHolmes is excited to be consulted about the latest strike of 'balloon man', a serial killer who focuses on children. Analyzing the crime scene, Holmes' deductions lead to the recovery of the first victim, Adam Kemper (then 12, now 19). However, Adam somberly refuses to help police find his captor and his latest victim.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-10-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2348774/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "The Rat Race", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nHolmes is hired by a Wall Street firm to find a missing executive. He finds the man, murdered, and then detects a pattern of mysterious deaths throughout the company's branches. But who could be benefiting from all of the murders?    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-10-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2360490/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Lesser Evils", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nDuring a visit to a hospital's morgue to do some experiments, Holmes deduces that a terminally ill patient has been murdered. Is this an isolated incident or is there an \"Angel of Mercy\" operating in the hospital?    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-11-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2459398/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Flight Risk", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nAfter a small jet crashes killing four people, Holmes battles both the police and the NTSB when he believes one of them was murdered before the crash occurred. Meanwhile, Watson confronts Holmes over a past friend, someone named Irene.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-11-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2473822/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "One Way to Get Off", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nSherlock identifies new murders as the modus operandi of Wade Crewes, the serial killer whose arrest made Captain Thomas Gregson's NYPD career. Their friendship is strained by necessary questions of whether it's a copycat, a former accomplice, or even the real serial killer. Worse yet, what if Crewes' initial conviction rested on a trumped-up investigation, notably by Gregson's partner at the time.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-11-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2481598/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "The Long Fuse", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nWhile Watson struggles with Holmes over finding a new sponsor, they work a case of a bombing of an Internet company. The bomb was planted four years ago but it's inconceivable that anyone would plan a bombing so far into the future.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-11-29", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2494318/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "You Do It to Yourself", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nOriental studies professor Trent Annunzio was killed with a bullet in each eye. Sherlock works out he was a Mahjong gambling addict and in which establishment, where he forces the owner to hand over secret video recordings. Those identify Raul Ramirez, but he was hired anonymously. prime suspect is Trent's academic assistant Brendan O'Brien, whose career he sabotages recently by recommending against an Ivy league promotion, and who has an affair with Trent's Thai wife Jun Annunzio. Sherlock works out the hidden truth and meanwhile gives Watson the decisive push to ...    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-12-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2517608/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "The Leviathan", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nMicah Erlich hires Holmes to solve urgently the robbery of diamonds in David Batonvert's Manhattan exchange from his world-reputed security firm's top-range vault model, the 'impregnable' Leviathan, before the news wrecks the manufacturer. Both men remember it was actually cracked once four years ago by a brilliant team of four, who were tried and jailed, but draw different conclusions concerning a connection, which Holmes has to revise while his investigation progresses with the help of his own consultants. Meanwhile he helps Watson deal with her unexpectedly ...    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2012-12-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2517610/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Dirty Laundry", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nThe manager of a high-end hotel that caters to diplomatic VIPs is found dead in the hotel's laundry. After first suspecting a connection to a prostitution ring, Holmes believes the answer lies in her treacherous past.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2570712/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "M.", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nSherlock is called in on a case and immediately recognizes the work of an old foe from Britain. Sherlock sees it as a chance at redemption in catching the man, but first he needs to control his own emotions about the murderer.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2579692/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "The Red Team", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nHolmes discovers a man running an internet conspiracy site is dead. As he follows the chain of clues, he becomes aware of the \"Red Team\" and the trail leads him further down the rabbit hole than he ever imagined.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-31", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2624868/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "The Deductionist", episode_number: "S1, Ep14", description: "\nA convicted killer who is supposed to donate a kidney to his sister ends up killing the surgical staff before escaping. Holmes is forced to work with a profiler (whom he can't stand) because she supposedly can predict what he will do next.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2624870/?ref_=ttep_ep14"},
  {title: "A Giant Gun, Filled with Drugs", episode_number: "S1, Ep15", description: "\nHolmes' former drug supplier comes to him for help to find his kidnapped daughter. He agrees to help him despite Watson's protests. When Holmes appears stymied, the former dealer encourages Holmes to go back on drugs, hoping it will help him solve the case.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2624872/?ref_=ttep_ep15"},
  {title: "Details", episode_number: "S1, Ep16", description: "\nDetective Bell is nearly killed while driving home one night. A just-released felon is the first suspect but, when he's killed, suspicion moves to Bell's brother who, unlike the dedicated detective, has lived life on the wrong side of the law.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2660926/?ref_=ttep_ep16"},
  {title: "Possibility Two", episode_number: "S1, Ep17", description: "\nA wealthy scientist comes to Holmes with a unique case: he believes he has been \"poisoned\" with a genetic disorder. Holmes has to determine how a healthy person can be contaminated with a genetic disease that no one in his family has.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2697934/?ref_=ttep_ep17"},
  {title: "Déjà Vu All Over Again", episode_number: "S1, Ep18", description: "\nWatson works a case on her own about a woman who has disappeared while Holmes deals with a subway murder. As they work their separate cases they gradually appear to be connected, even though they can't determine exactly how.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-03-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2729080/?ref_=ttep_ep18"},
  {title: "Snow Angels", episode_number: "S1, Ep19", description: "\nIn the middle of a winter storm, Holmes and Watson must solve the murder of a guard during a botched robbery and unravel the killer's true plan. The pair also get an interesting new roommate.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2733692/?ref_=ttep_ep19"},
  {title: "Dead Man's Switch", episode_number: "S1, Ep20", description: "\nA blackmailer uses tapes of underage girls to get money from their fathers. When Holmes witnesses the blackmailer's murder, it becomes a race to find out who his accomplice is and prevent the videos from being released on the Internet.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2778808/?ref_=ttep_ep20"},
  {title: "A Landmark Story", episode_number: "S1, Ep21", description: "\nA man connected to the classification of a valuable building as a landmark trust dies when his pacemaker is deliberately short circuited. Holmes soon learns the one behind the murder is an old nemesis known to him only as \"Moriarty\".    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-05-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2778806/?ref_=ttep_ep21"},
  {title: "Risk Management", episode_number: "S1, Ep22", description: "\nMoriarty asks Holmes to find out who murdered a mechanic in Brooklyn. Despite Watson's protests, Holmes thinks this case will help him uncover Moriarty's true identity, but it will, in fact, lead Holmes to something much worse.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-05-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2778816/?ref_=ttep_ep22"},
  {title: "The Woman", episode_number: "S1, Ep23", description: "\nHolmes reconnects with Irene, his one true love that he thought had been taken from him by Moriarity. He tries to protect her as she recovers from her trauma but he soon learns that it isn't she that needs protection.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-05-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2767596/?ref_=ttep_ep23"},
  {title: "Heroine", episode_number: "S1, Ep24", description: "\nWhile recovering from his gun shot wounds, Holmes eschews painkillers while working on a case of a Greek shipping magnate - involving an assassination and currency manipulation - before his final showdown with Moriarty.    ", season_id: 2589, series_id: 45, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-05-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2767598/?ref_=ttep_ep24"},
  {title: "Glanders", episode_number: "S4, Ep1", description: "\nSeason 4 opens with Martha upset when Philip relates Gene's role in protecting her. The trip to Germany has repercussions for the Jennings family. Gabriel tells Elizabeth and Philip about William, who has samples of US biological weaponry, which they are to acquire. Back in USSR, Nina continues to leech onto Anton for her own freedom ...or does she have another agenda? Pastor Tom continues to pry information out of a guilty and confused Paige, but they do not know the phone is bugged. Philip and Elizabeth have numerous problems meeting William without a tail. Either ...    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4573270/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Pastor Tim", episode_number: "S4, Ep2", description: "\nPhilip tries with increasing desperation to get rid of a sensitive and dangerous package as family tensions in the Jennings House reach a boiling point when Paige shares a secret of her own.    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5183578/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Experimental Prototype City of Tomorrow", episode_number: "S4, Ep3", description: "\nPaige copes with new burdens that come with her family's secret - as Philip and Elizabeth struggle to contain their cover without destroying their daughter.    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-03-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5124962/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Chloramphenicol", episode_number: "S4, Ep4", description: "\nA devastating flaw during a mission forces Philip, Elizabeth, William, and Gabriel to confront the depths of their patriotism... and their mortality. In Russia, in striving to be a better person, has Nina put her life on the line?    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5255258/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Clark's Place", episode_number: "S4, Ep5", description: "\nPhilip must consider his life with Martha and make a crushing choice from which there is no coming back.    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5253620/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "The Rat", episode_number: "S4, Ep6", description: "\nMartha must finally face the truth she has denied - and her life may never be the same. Plus, a chilling new development in William's work forces the Jennings to face the realities of what a biological war would mean.    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5339002/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Travel Agents", episode_number: "S4, Ep7", description: "\nMartha must finally face the truth she has denied - and her life may never be the same. Plus, a chilling new development in William's work forces the Jennings to face the realities of what a biological war would mean.    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-04-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5374770/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "The Magic of David Copperfield V: The Statue of Liberty Disappears", episode_number: "S4, Ep8", description: "\nThe Jennings hit their breaking points as they try to handle their local agents such as Martha.    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5562344/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "The Day After", episode_number: "S4, Ep9", description: "\nThe Day After premieres, making the stakes - and terrible consequences - of the Cold War plain. Even with that in mind, will Elizabeth be able to complete the painful process of the \"Patty\" operation?    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5339026/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Munchkins", episode_number: "S4, Ep10", description: "\nWhen Paige's long-ago indiscretion threatens to resurface and destroy the family, Philip and Elizabeth find themselves scrambling - and Paige finds herself reevaluating who her parents really are.    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5449928/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Dinner for Seven", episode_number: "S4, Ep11", description: "\nElizabeth completes the last steps of a very personal operation... but at what cost?    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-05-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5478564/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "A Roy Rogers in Franconia", episode_number: "S4, Ep12", description: "\nAs Paige deals with last episode's trauma, she sees her mother in a new light... and finds she has inherited some of her parents' skills. Plus, has Oleg reached his breaking point with Stan?    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-06-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt5339034/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Persona Non Grata", episode_number: "S4, Ep13", description: "\nIn the season 4 finale, Elizabeth & Philip race against the FBI to retrieve a mysterious package. Paige finally begins considering whether or not she would like to enter the family business.    ", season_id: 2590, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2016-06-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4759442/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "EST Men", episode_number: "S3, Ep1", description: "\nThings are tense between Elizabeth and Philip as they have differing opinions over how to handle orders coming from the Centre.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-01-28", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3672866/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Baggage", episode_number: "S3, Ep2", description: "\nStabler is forced to work on a serial killer case with an abrasive detective who has been on the case for months and would prefer to work alone. However, Stabler discovers that the detective's motivation is not glory and recognition.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2009-04-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4183010/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Open House", episode_number: "S3, Ep3", description: "\nElizabeth and Philip get closer to the inner circle of the C.I.A. Afghan Group.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4303066/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "Dimebag", episode_number: "S3, Ep4", description: "\nPhilip faces a moral dilemma while developing an asset; Paige makes a surprising birthday wish.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4259458/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Salang Pass", episode_number: "S3, Ep5", description: "\nPhilip juggles the many women in his life; Elizabeth takes drastic measures to complete a mission.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-02-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4228750/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Born Again", episode_number: "S3, Ep6", description: "\nGabriel has surprising information; Elizabeth begins to take family matters into her own hands.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-04", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4259460/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Walter Taffet", episode_number: "S3, Ep7", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth feel the weight of a family secret while following up on the KGB's interests.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-11", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4277628/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Divestment", episode_number: "S3, Ep8", description: "\nMartha and Clark's marriage meets its most challenging test yet; pressure on Philip intensifies.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-18", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4257820/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Do Mail Robots Dream of Electric Sheep?", episode_number: "S3, Ep9", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth struggle with the gravity of unexpected collateral damage.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-03-25", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4343722/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Stingers", episode_number: "S3, Ep10", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth deploy a plan for the C.I.A.'s Mujahideen visitors.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4331672/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "One Day in the Life of Anton Baklanov", episode_number: "S3, Ep11", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth's home and work lives collide in new and dangerous ways. Nina struggles to figure out her next steps. Arkady assigns Oleg and Tatiana to an operation with uncertain potential.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-08", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4458716/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "I Am Abassin Zadran", episode_number: "S3, Ep12", description: "\nMartha hosts an unexpected guest; Philip and Elizabeth must work a formidable Mujahideen commander.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-15", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4428472/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "March 8, 1983", episode_number: "S3, Ep13", description: "\nElizabeth and Paige take a trip that lands them in treacherous territory.    ", season_id: 2591, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2015-04-22", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt4419730/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Comrades", episode_number: "S2, Ep1", description: "\nElizabeth comes back from her injury and straight into what should have been a routine mission - but it goes awry, leaving her and Philip in fear not only for themselves but for their whole network... and family. Paige's suspicions have only grown in her mother's absence. Meanwhile, Stan continues to fall for the Russian agent who has started to play him.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-02-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2726822/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "Cardinal", episode_number: "S2, Ep2", description: "\nAs Philip investigates the fallout from the last operation, Elizabeth sticks close to home, concerned for her family until she gets a mysterious distress signal. Meanwhile, a walk-in arrives at the Rezidentura - providing both Nina and Stan with unique opportunities.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-05", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3459856/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "The Walk-In", episode_number: "S2, Ep3", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth complete their next mission - but not without complications - and Philip's fears about Elizabeth's readiness for action deepen. Stan tracks the KGB walk-in which leads to much praise at work and a deepening of his attachment to, and dependence on, Nina. Meanwhile, Paige snoops into her mother's family background and Oleg begins to scrutinize Nina's secret operation.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-12", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3459862/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "A Little Night Music", episode_number: "S2, Ep4", description: "\nJust when Philip and Elizabeth think they have a quiet road ahead, an old friend returns to complicate things. Not only do they have to intercept a target who could prove valuable to the Soviet Union, but they also have to take on an important rogue mission without the support of the Centre. Divisions inside the Rezidentura deepen between Oleg and Arkady and there's an upheaval at the FBI as the chickens come home to roost for Agent Gaad. Meanwhile, Martha's frustrations threaten to blow Philip's cover.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-19", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3459860/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "The Deal", episode_number: "S2, Ep5", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth are finally assigned a new handler as Philip works to clean up the mess of the last operation and Elizabeth, in disguise as Clark's sister Jennifer, does her best to smooth things over with Martha. As Stan searches for a missing scientist, Oleg and Arkady continue to argue over how best to handle the situation on their side, leaving Nina once again caught between the FBI and KGB.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-03-26", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3459858/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Behind the Red Door", episode_number: "S2, Ep6", description: "\nA dangerous Naval officer becomes the key to Philip and Elizabeth's mission as well as a potential threat to their family's safety. Lucia, a Sandinista intelligence officer working with the Jennings, is tasked with getting Elizabeth access to Capitol Hill. Stan struggles with the potential costs of protecting Nina.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-02", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3459866/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Arpanet", episode_number: "S2, Ep7", description: "\nPhilip uses his agent Charles Duluth to help him gain access to an early precursor to the Internet so that the KGB can bug American government communications. Nina faces the threat of a potential FBI polygraph exam, bringing her closer to KGB colleague Oleg.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-09", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3459864/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "New Car", episode_number: "S2, Ep8", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth both find themselves faced with painful turns in their various missions. Stan fights to gain access to an American military program that could give him the upper hand in his battle of wills with Oleg.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-16", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3533366/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Martial Eagle", episode_number: "S2, Ep9", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth's long-planned mission turns ugly, impacting each of them in different ways. Stan digs in deeper at work as his personal life continues to unravel.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-23", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3553756/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Yousaf", episode_number: "S2, Ep10", description: "\nA new mission with international stakes has Philip calling on Annelise for assistance just as an old foe returns to D.C. with a vendetta. Stan makes a discovery that could put the FBI hot on the trail of illegals.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-04-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3594864/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Stealth", episode_number: "S2, Ep11", description: "\nElizabeth makes a shocking discovery about Kate. Philip pursues a contact for information about the new Stealth technology. Stan continues his pursuit of the illegals.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-07", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3594870/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "Operation Chronicle", episode_number: "S2, Ep12", description: "\nWith Larrick closing in, Elizabeth rushes to exfiltrate Jared while Philip readies Fred for a crucial mission. Arkady finally plays his hand, forcing Stan to make an impossible choice.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-14", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3594868/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "Echo", episode_number: "S2, Ep13", description: "\nNina finds that her future is Stan's hands. Meanwhile, Paige and Henry are moved to safety as their parents attempt to complete their assignment.    ", season_id: 2592, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2014-05-21", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt3599846/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
  {title: "Pilot", episode_number: "S1, Ep1", description: "\nPhillip and Elizabeth Jennings are two seemingly normal Americans who are really undercover KGB agents. After kidnapping a Soviet defector they discover their new neighbor is an FBI agent assigned to their case.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-01-30", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2349740/?ref_=ttep_ep1"},
  {title: "The Clock", episode_number: "S1, Ep2", description: "\nWhen Philip and Elizabeth are given an urgent task to plant a bug in Defense Secretary Caspar Weinberger's office, they risk exposure when an unwilling maid of the Weinberger home refuses to cooperate.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2573020/?ref_=ttep_ep2"},
  {title: "Gregory", episode_number: "S1, Ep3", description: "\nGregory, Elizabeth's lover, helps them make contact with Robert's widow despite an FBI team. Gabriel's replacement shows up. Phillip then makes a dangerous buy of information.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2598996/?ref_=ttep_ep3"},
  {title: "In Control", episode_number: "S1, Ep4", description: "\nAfter President Reagan is nearly assassinated events quickly start to spin out of control. The FBI wonders if the KGB is somehow behind it; the KGB worry that they will be blamed for it and possibly result in war.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2637674/?ref_=ttep_ep4"},
  {title: "Comint", episode_number: "S1, Ep5", description: "\nA crucial agent crumbles under emotional distress and threatens to topple a valuable network of KGB informants.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-02-27", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2637678/?ref_=ttep_ep5"},
  {title: "Trust Me", episode_number: "S1, Ep6", description: "\nA mole hunt within the KGB causes suspicion amongst allies and shatters trust within the Jennings' marriage. Meanwhile, Stan's plan to keep his mole safe puts her at even greater risk of discovery.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-03-06", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2637676/?ref_=ttep_ep6"},
  {title: "Duty and Honor", episode_number: "S1, Ep7", description: "\nPhilip and Elizabeth's troubled marriage is further tested when a mission to discredit a Polish pro-democracy leader reunites Philip with his old flame.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-03-13", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2637680/?ref_=ttep_ep7"},
  {title: "Mutually Assured Destruction", episode_number: "S1, Ep8", description: "\nA German assassin has been ordered to kill American scientists involved in the ABM program. After the mission is aborted, Phillip and Elizabeth must stop him and prevent a possible war, without having any idea of his identity.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-03-20", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2637682/?ref_=ttep_ep8"},
  {title: "Safe House", episode_number: "S1, Ep9", description: "\nPhillip and Elizabeth shock their children when they announce they are separating. After Amador goes missing, Gaad orders an unauthorized mission to grab a KGB agent in retaliation. Events soon spin out of control and come to a grisly end.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-03", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2737870/?ref_=ttep_ep9"},
  {title: "Only You", episode_number: "S1, Ep10", description: "\nAfter Amador's murder the FBI begins a massive manhunt for the killer. When they start closing in on Gregory, the KGB decides to send him to Moscow. Despite Elizabeth's best efforts he refuses to go, even if it means his life.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-10", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2737872/?ref_=ttep_ep10"},
  {title: "Covert War", episode_number: "S1, Ep11", description: "\nIn Moscow, Viktor Zhukov is assassinated in the escalating tensions between the two countries. When Elizabeth learns that her personal mentor has been murdered she risks everything to avenge his death.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-17", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2737878/?ref_=ttep_ep11"},
  {title: "The Oath", episode_number: "S1, Ep12", description: "\nAn Air Force colonel offers to sell SDI secrets to the KGB. Viola reports the bug in the Weinberger home. Phillip agrees to marry Martha hoping she'll continue spying while Nina confesses to spying for the Americans.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-04-24", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2737876/?ref_=ttep_ep12"},
  {title: "The Colonel", episode_number: "S1, Ep13", description: "\nElizabeth and Phillip are at risk of getting caught when they fear their assignments may be a set-up. Stan is convinced he'll find Nina a way out.    ", season_id: 2593, series_id: 46, season_episode_number: nil, air_date: "2013-05-01", seasonno: nil, url: "/title/tt2737880/?ref_=ttep_ep13"},
